#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kmail;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kmail;-a"

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main Window"
msgstr "Okno Bralnika Pošte"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main window is the window that appears when &kmail; is started. It is by "
"default divided into three panes:"
msgstr ""
"Glavno okno je okno, ki se prikaže ob zagonu programa &kmail;. Privzeto je "
"razdeljeno na tri okna:"

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder List (on the left)"
msgstr "Seznam Map (na levi)"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: using-kmail.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Folder Pane</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pult mapa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: using-kmail.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Folder Pane</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pult mapa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Folder List"
msgstr "Seznam map"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:50 using-kmail.docbook:63 using-kmail.docbook:84
#: using-kmail.docbook:105 using-kmail.docbook:125 using-kmail.docbook:354
#: using-kmail.docbook:442 using-kmail.docbook:455 using-kmail.docbook:518
#: using-kmail.docbook:543 using-kmail.docbook:688 using-kmail.docbook:734
#: using-kmail.docbook:767 using-kmail.docbook:792 using-kmail.docbook:811
#: using-kmail.docbook:877 using-kmail.docbook:1147 using-kmail.docbook:1200
#: using-kmail.docbook:1323 using-kmail.docbook:1514 using-kmail.docbook:1741
#: using-kmail.docbook:1874
#, no-c-format
msgid "&nbsp;"
msgstr "&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This pane contains the list of your message folders (other email programs "
"may call them mailboxes). To select a folder, simply click on it. The "
"message header information contained in the folder will then appear in the "
"Message List pane. The folder list can be displayed in both a short view, "
"which takes up only a small portion of the left side of the screen, and a "
"long view, which takes up the entire left side of the screen (and can show "
"more folders). You can toggle between these two views by using the "
"<guilabel>Appearance</guilabel>/<guilabel>Layout</guilabel> tab in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kmail;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog. The top section of the folder pane "
"provides quick links to your favorite folders. Drag and drop folders here, "
"or add them via the &RMB; context menu item <guimenuitem>Add Favorite "
"Folder</guimenuitem>. Please see the <link linkend=\"folders\">Folders "
"Section</link> for more details about folders."
msgstr ""
"To podokno vsebuje seznam map za sporočila (drugi e-poštni programi jih "
"lahko imenujejo poštni predali). Če želite izbrati mapo, kliknite nanjo. "
"Informacije v glavi sporočila, ki jih vsebuje mapa, bodo nato prikazane v "
"podoknu Seznam sporočil. Seznam map je lahko prikazan v kratkem pogledu, ki "
"zavzema le majhen del leve strani zaslona, in dolgem pogledu, ki zavzema "
"celotno levo stran zaslona (in lahko prikaže več map). Med tema dvema "
"pogledoma lahko preklapljate z uporabo zavihka <guilabel>Videz</guilabel>/"
"<guilabel>Razporeditev</guilabel> v oknu <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavitve &kmail;-a...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. V "
"zgornjem delu podokna z mapami so na voljo hitre povezave do priljubljenih "
"map. Sem povlecite in spustite mape ali jih dodajte prek elementa &RMB; "
"kontekstnega menija <guimenuitem>Dodaj priljubljeno mapo</guimenuitem>. Za "
"več podrobnosti o mapah glejte <link linkend=\"folders\">Poglavje o mapah</"
"link>."

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message List (on the upper right by default)"
msgstr "Seznam sporočil (privzeto zgoraj desno)"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: using-kmail.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Message List</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Seznam sporočil</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: using-kmail.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Message List</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Seznam sporočil</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Message List (Smart Theme)"
msgstr "Seznam sporočil (pametna tema)"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This pane lists header information (Subject, Sender, and Date) for the "
"messages in the currently selected folder. Clicking on an item in the "
"Message List will select that message and display it in the Preview pane; "
"you can also select more than one message by holding down the &Ctrl; key (or "
"the &Shift; key) when clicking on messages."
msgstr ""
"V tem podoknu so navedeni podatki v glavi (Zadeva, Pošiljatelj in Datum) za "
"sporočila v trenutno izbrani mapi. S klikom na element na seznamu sporočil "
"boste izbrali to sporočilo in ga prikazali v podoknu za predogled; izberete "
"lahko tudi več kot eno sporočilo, tako da med klikanjem na sporočila držite "
"pritisnjeno tipko &Ctrl; (ali tipko &Shift;)."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the appearance of your message list by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Message List</guimenuitem> "
"<guimenuitem>Theme</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. You have several options here."
msgstr ""
"Videz seznama sporočil spremenite tako, da izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Seznam sporočil</"
"guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Tema</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Na voljo imate "
"več možnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Classic</guilabel> A simple, backward compatible single row with "
"clickable sort columns."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Klasična</guilabel> Enostavna, nazaj združljiva ena vrstica s "
"stolpci za razvrščanje s klikom."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Smart</guilabel> A smart multi-line, multi-item list with status "
"icons, and no sort columns."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pametna</guilabel> Pametni večvrstični seznam z ikonami stanja in "
"brez stolpcev za razvrščanje."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Smart with Clickable Status</guilabel> A smart multi-line, multi-"
"item list with clickable status icons."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pametna, s stanji, ki jih je mogoče klikati</guilabel> Pametni "
"večvrstični seznam z več postavkami in ikonami statusa s klikom."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Configure...</guilabel> Allows you to customize your own Message "
"List Theme (&eg; add or remove columns from the clickable sort bar.)"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Nastavi...</guilabel> Omogoča vam, da prilagodite svojo temo "
"seznama sporočil (&eg; dodajanje ali odstranjevanje stolpcev iz vrstice za "
"razvrščanje, ki jo je mogoče klikati.)"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have chosen the Classic theme, you may sort the messages by clicking "
"on the column that you wish to sort; if you click on the same column again, "
"the sort order will toggle between ascending/descending. Clicking the &RMB; "
"on the list header shows a pop up menu, which allows you to show or hide "
"several columns in the list. You can customize the columns visible on the "
"sort bar; see <link linkend=\"customize-messagelist-theme\">Configure "
"Appearance of Message List</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Če ste izbrali klasično temo, lahko sporočila razvrstite tako, da kliknete "
"na stolpec, ki ga želite razvrstiti; če ponovno kliknete na isti stolpec, se "
"vrstni red preklopi med naraščajočim in padajočim. S klikom na &RMB; na "
"glavi seznama se prikaže priročni meni, ki omogoča prikaz ali skritje več "
"stolpcev na seznamu. Prilagodite lahko stolpce, ki so vidni v vrstici za "
"razvrščanje; za podrobnosti glejte <link linkend=\"customize-messagelist-"
"theme\">Nastavi videz seznama sporočil</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview Pane (in the lower right by default)"
msgstr "Predogledni pult (privzeto spodaj desno)"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: using-kmail.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Message Preview Pane</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pult za predogled sporočil</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: using-kmail.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Message Preview Pane</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pult za predogled sporočil</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Preview Pane"
msgstr "Pult za predogled"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This pane displays the currently selected message. Here are some ways to "
"adjust the Preview pane."
msgstr ""
"V tem podoknu je prikazano trenutno izbrano sporočilo. Tukaj je nekaj "
"načinov za prilagoditev podokna Predogled."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top of the Preview pane displays the message headers. Several display "
"options are available. Go to <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Headers</guisubmenu></menuchoice> and try them out until "
"you find one you like!"
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu podokna Predogled so prikazane glave sporočila. Na voljo je več "
"možnosti prikaza. Pojdite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Glave</guisubmenu></menuchoice> in jih preizkušajte, "
"dokler ne najdete tiste, ki vam je všeč!"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Fancy Headers</guilabel> Colorful header with a spam status / "
"attachments notification."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Razkošne glave</guilabel> Barvita glava z obvestilom o stanju "
"neželene pošte / priponkah."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Brief Headers</guilabel> Title, and in parentheses: From, CCs (if "
"any), and the date."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kratke glave</guilabel> Naslov in v oklepaju: Od, CC (če "
"obstajajo) in datum."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>&kmail; 5.2</guilabel> An avatar (if available) with Title, From, "
"To, CCs (if any), and spam status / attachments on separate lines."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>&kmail; 5.2</guilabel> Avatar (če je na voljo) s Predmetom, Od, "
"Za, Kp (če je), and statusom neželenega sporočila / priloge v ločenih "
"vrsticah."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Download New Themes...</guilabel> Allows you to download custom "
"themes created by other &kmail; users."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prenesi nove teme...</guilabel> Omogoča prenos tem po meri, ki so "
"jih ustvarili drugi uporabniki &kmail;."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the bar located on the left hand side of the pane to toggle between "
"plain text and &HTML; (if and only if the message is coded both ways). The "
"text on the bar will inform you which view you are in. The "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kmail;...</"
"guimenuitem><guisubmenu>Security</guisubmenu></menuchoice> dialog allows you "
"to select HTML as the default message display option, if you prefer &HTML; "
"to plain text."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na vrstico na levi strani podokna lahko preklapljate med navadnim "
"besedilom in &HTML; (če in samo če je sporočilo kodirano na oba načina). "
"Besedilo v vrstici vas bo obvestilo, v katerem pogledu se nahajate. V "
"pogovornem oknu <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavitve &kmail;-a...</"
"guimenuitem><guisubmenu>Varnost</guisubmenu></menuchoice> lahko izberete "
"HTML kot privzeto možnost za prikaz sporočil, če imate raje &HTML; kot "
"navadno besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you would like to change the way your attachments appear in your "
"messages, go to <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Attachments</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>. These are your options."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti način prikazovanja priponk v sporočilih, pojdite na "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Priponke</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>. To so vaše možnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>As Icons</guimenuitem>, all attachments appear as icons at the "
"bottom of the message."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Kot ikone</guimenuitem>, vse priponke se prikažejo kot ikone na "
"dnu sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Smart</guimenuitem> will show attachments as icons, unless the "
"message suggests that they should be displayed inline. You can suggest that "
"certain attachments should be shown inline in messages you compose by "
"selecting <guilabel>Suggest automatic display</guilabel> in <link linkend="
"\"the-composer-window\">the composer window</link> via the attachment's "
"properties dialog."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Pametno</guimenuitem> bo priponke prikazal kot ikone, razen če "
"sporočilo nakazuje, da naj bodo prikazane v vrstici. Določene priloge lahko "
"predlagate, da se prikažejo v vrstici v sestavljenih sporočilih, tako da v "
"<link linkend=\"the-composer-window\">oknu skladatelja</link> v pogovornem "
"oknu lastnosti priloge izberete možnost <guilabel>Predlagaj samodejni "
"prikaz</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Inline</guimenuitem> shows the contents of the attachments at "
"the bottom of the message. Attachments that cannot be displayed, &eg; "
"compressed files, will still be shown as an icon."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Znotrajvrstično</guimenuitem> prikaže vsebino priponk na dnu "
"sporočila. Priloge, ki jih ni mogoče prikazati, npr. stisnjene datoteke, "
"bodo še vedno prikazane kot ikona."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Hide</guimenuitem> will not show attachments."
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Skrij</guimenuitem> ne prikaže priponk."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>In Header Only</guimenuitem> will suppress inline displays, but "
"list the attachments along with the message headers."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Samo v glavi</guimenuitem> bo onemogočil prikaze v vrstici, "
"vendar bo priponke navedel skupaj z glavo sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The interactions among the header themes, the attachment views, and the "
"plain text versus &HTML; preferences is rather complex. For example, if you "
"attach an HTML file to a plain text message, &kmail; will probably interpret "
"your message as being coded in two different formats, even though this is "
"not really the case. Similarly, &HTML; messages may display embedded images "
"even when you have selected the \"Hide\" option for attachments."
msgstr ""
"Vzajemno delovanje tem glave, pogledov na priponke in nastavitev navadnega "
"besedila v primerjavi z &HTML; je precej zapleteno. Na primer, če boste "
"navadnemu besedilnemu sporočilu priložili datoteko HTML, bo &kmail; vaše "
"sporočilo verjetno razumel, kot da je kodirano v dveh različnih formatih, "
"čeprav temu v resnici ni tako. Podobno se lahko v sporočilih &HTML; "
"prikažejo vstavljene slike, tudi če ste za priponke izbrali možnost \"Skrij"
"\"."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The structure of each message can be displayed by pressing <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>. This will open a message "
"structure viewer below the preview pane. Turn the message structure viewer "
"off by pressing the same three keys."
msgstr ""
"Strukturo vsakega sporočila lahko prikažete tako, da pritisnete <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>. Tako se bo pod "
"podoknom za predogled odprl pregledovalnik strukture sporočila. S pritiskom "
"istih treh tipk izklopite pregledovalnik strukture sporočil."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can scroll through the message page-by-page using the &PgUp; and &PgDn; "
"keys, or line-by-line using the &Up; and &Down; keys; you can also use <link "
"linkend=\"keyboard-shortcuts\">keyboard shortcuts</link> to skip through "
"your messages without having to use the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Po sporočilih se lahko pomikate stran za stranjo s tipkama &PgUp; in &PgDn; "
"ali vrstico za vrstico s tipkama &Up; in &Down; uporabite lahko tudi <link "
"linkend=\"keyboard-shortcuts\">skrajšave na tipkovnici</link>, da preskočite "
"sporočila brez uporabe miške."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Shortcuts"
msgstr "Tipkovne bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following keyboard shortcuts are supported by default in the main "
"window. Notice that many \"universal\" shortcuts (&eg; <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> to copy selected text to the "
"clipboard, or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> "
"to open a \"Find\" dialog) are recognized by &kmail;, but are not documented "
"here."
msgstr ""
"V glavnem oknu so privzeto podprte naslednje bližnjice na tipkovnici. "
"Upoštevajte, da &kmail; prepozna številne \"univerzalne\" bližnjice (&eg; "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> za kopiranje "
"izbranega besedila v odložišče ali <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> za odprtje pogovornega okna \"Najdi\"), ki pa "
"tukaj niso dokumentirane."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Shortcut"
msgstr "Tipka z Bližnjico"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "Action"
msgstr "Dejanje"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Space;"
msgstr "&Space;"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scroll down in the current message."
msgstr "Podrsaj navzdol po trenutnem sporočilu."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>→</keycap> or <keycap>N</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>→</keycap> ali <keycap>N</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the next message in the current folder and display the message preview."
msgstr "Naslednje sporočilo v trenutni mapi in prikaz predogleda sporočila."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>←</keycap> or <keycap>P</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>←</keycap> ali <keycap>P</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the previous message in the current folder and display the message "
"preview."
msgstr "Prejšnje sporočilo v trenutni mapi in prikaz predogleda spročila."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:203 using-kmail.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Home;"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Home;"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the very first message in the current folder and display the message "
"preview."
msgstr "Prvo sporočilo v trenutni mapi in prikaz predogleda sporočila."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:207 using-kmail.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&End;"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&End;"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the very last message in the current folder and display the message "
"preview."
msgstr "Zadnje sporočilo v trenutni mapi in prikaz predogleda sporočila."

#. Tag: keycap
#: using-kmail.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>+</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>+</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next unread message in the current folder."
msgstr "Naslednje neprebrano sporočilo v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: keycap
#: using-kmail.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>-</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>-</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the previous unread message in the current folder."
msgstr "Prejšnje neprebrano sporočilo v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: keycap
#: using-kmail.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>C</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>C</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy this message to another folder."
msgstr "Kopiraj to sporočilo v drugo mapo."

#. Tag: keycap
#: using-kmail.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>M</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>M</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move this message to another folder."
msgstr "Premakni to sporočilo v drugo mapo."

#. Tag: keycap
#: using-kmail.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>A</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>A</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reply to all recipients of this message (with quote)."
msgstr "Odgovori sem prejemnikom tega spročila (s citiranim besedilom)"

#. Tag: keycap
#: using-kmail.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>R</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>R</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reply to sender with quote."
msgstr "Odgovori pošiljatelju s citiranim besedilom."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap>"
msgstr "&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reply to sender without quoting anything."
msgstr "Odgovori pošiljatelju brez citiranja."

#. Tag: keycap
#: using-kmail.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>S</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>S</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Launch the message search dialog."
msgstr "Zažene pogovorno okno za iskanje sporočil."

#. Tag: keycap
#: using-kmail.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>T</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>T</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open this message in the composition window."
msgstr "Odpre to sporočilo v oknu skladatelja."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Enter;"
msgstr "&Enter;"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "View selected message in the full-screen message viewer."
msgstr "Oglejte si izbrano sporočilo v celozaslonskem načinu."

#. Tag: keycap
#: using-kmail.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>V</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>V</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "View the raw message, headers and all, as a text file."
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si surovo sporočilo z vključenimi glavami in vsem ostalim kot "
"besedilno datoteko."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check for new messages on the server(s)."
msgstr "Preveri za nova sporočila na strežnikih."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the composition window to write a new message."
msgstr "Če želite napisati novo sporočilo, odprite okno za sestavljanje."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zoom in on the current message, in increments of 20%."
msgstr "Približaj trenutno sporočilo, v korakih po 20%."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zoom out of the current message, in increments of 20%."
msgstr "Oddalji pogled na trenutno sporočilo, v korakih po 20%."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>0</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>0</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reset message Zoom factor to 100% (full size)."
msgstr "Ponastav pogled na 100% (pričakovano velikost)"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle message structure display (below the message preview pane)."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite prikaz strukture sporočila (pod podoknom za predogled sporočila)."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create the tabbing toolbar (appears above the message list)."
msgstr "Ustvarite orodno vrstico z zavihki (prikaže se nad seznamom sporočil)."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>W</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>W</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove the currently active tab from the tabbing toolbar."
msgstr "Odstranite trenutno aktivni zavihek iz orodne vrstice z zavihki."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Alt;<keycap>↑</keycap>"
msgstr "&Alt;<keycap>↑</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the previous folder in the folder list (if the folder list has focus)."
msgstr "Pojdite na prejšnjo mapo na seznamu map (če je seznam map v žarišču)."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Alt;<keycap>↓</keycap>"
msgstr "&Alt;<keycap>↓</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the next folder in the folder list (if the folder list has focus)."
msgstr "Pojdite na naslednjo mapo na seznamu map (če je seznam map v žarišču)."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus on the very first folder. Use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Space;"
"</keycombo> to actually enter the folder."
msgstr ""
"Postavite prvo mapo v žarišče. Uporabite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Space;</keycombo>, da dejansko vstopite v mapo."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus on the very last folder. Use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Space;</"
"keycombo> to actually enter the folder."
msgstr ""
"Naj bo zadnja mapa v žarišču. Uporabite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Space;</keycombo>, da dejansko vstopite v mapo."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Space;"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Space;"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the folder that has focus, &ie; the folder that you navigated to using "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Home;</keycombo> or <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite mapo, ki je v žarišču, &ie; mapo, do katere ste krenili z uporabo "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Home;</keycombo> ali <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo>."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: using-kmail.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift;<keycap>H</keycap>"
msgstr "&Shift;<keycap>H</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle between plain text and &HTML; (unless &HTML; has been preferred via "
"the <guilabel>Settings</guilabel> dialog)."
msgstr ""
"Preklapljanje med navadnim besedilom in &HTML; (razen če ste v pogovornem "
"oknu <guilabel>Nastavitve</guilabel> dali prednost &HTML;)."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>←</keycap></keycombo> &amp; "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>→</keycap></keycombo>"
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>←</keycap></keycombo> &amp; "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>→</keycap></keycombo>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select messages sequentially in the message list, starting with the current "
"message."
msgstr ""
"Sporočila na seznamu sporočil izbirate zaporedno, začenši s trenutnim "
"sporočilom."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more keyboard shortcuts, take a look at the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog. If you're not happy with the defaults, you "
"can change them!"
msgstr ""
"Za več bližnjic na tipkovnici si oglejte pogovorno okno "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavljanje "
"bližnjic...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če niste zadovoljni s privzetimi "
"nastavitvami, jih lahko spremenite!"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Two mouse actions deserve mention here. First, you can select multiple "
"noncontiguous messages to be processed all at once (&eg; copied, deleted, or "
"moved) by pressing &Ctrl; and selecting them with the &LMB;. Second, you can "
"open a message in an external window by double-clicking an item in the "
"message list. If the message is in the outbox, drafts, or templates folder, "
"it will be opened in a composition window. Otherwise, it will be opened with "
"the external message viewer, an abbreviated version of &kmail;'s main window "
"without the folder and message lists, and with shorter menus."
msgstr ""
"Tu je treba omeniti dve dejanji z miško. Najprej lahko izberete več "
"nesorodnih sporočil, ki jih želite obdelati naenkrat (kopiranje, brisanje "
"ali premikanje), tako da pritisnete &Ctrl; in jih izberete z &LMB;. Drugič, "
"sporočilo lahko odprete v zunanjem oknu tako, da dvakrat kliknete element na "
"seznamu sporočil. Če je sporočilo v mapi Prejeto, Osnutki ali Predloge, se "
"odpre v oknu za sestavljanje. V nasprotnem primeru se odpre z zunanjim "
"pregledovalnikom sporočil, skrajšano različico glavnega okna &kmail;-a brez "
"seznama map in sporočil ter s krajšimi meniji."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Composer Window"
msgstr "Okno Sestavljalnika"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: using-kmail.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Composer Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Okno skladatelja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: using-kmail.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Composer Window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Okno skladatelja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Composer Window in &HTML; composition mode."
msgstr "Okno skladatelja v načinu sestave &HTML;."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The composer window is used to write new messages, to compose replies, and "
"to forward messages. It can be opened in several ways. Here are the various "
"options for composing messages."
msgstr ""
"Okno za sestavljanje se uporablja za pisanje novih sporočil, sestavljanje "
"odgovorov in posredovanje sporočil. Odprete ga lahko na več načinov. Tukaj "
"so različne možnosti za sestavljanje sporočil."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Composing a Message"
msgstr "Sestavljanje Sporočila"

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Message..."
msgstr "Novo sporočilo..."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "The New Message composer window can be invoked in four different ways:"
msgstr ""
"Okno Skladtelj novega sporočila lahko prikličete na štiri različne načine:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kmail.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>New "
"Message...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Novo</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Novo "
"sporočilo...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kmail.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Message...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo sporočilo...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Via the <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-"
"message-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> New</"
"guiicon> icon on the main toolbar."
msgstr ""
"S pomočjo ikone <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"mail-message-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Novo</guiicon> v glavni orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Via the keyboard shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</"
"keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Preko tipkovne bližnjice <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</"
"keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To write your message, fill in the appropriate fields in the composer "
"window. Use the <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu to select which header fields "
"are displayed. Any selection you make will remain as the default when you "
"open a new composer window. These items are available."
msgstr ""
"Če želite napisati sporočilo, v oknu za sestavljanje izpolnite ustrezna "
"polja. Z menijem <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> lahko izberete, katera polja "
"glave so prikazana. Izbrana izbira bo ostala privzeta, ko odprete novo okno "
"skladatelja. Ti elementi so na voljo."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Identity</guimenuitem> drop down box lets you select an "
"identity to use."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem oknu <guimenuitem>Identiteta</guimenuitem> lahko izberete "
"identiteto, ki jo želite uporabiti."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Dictionary</guimenuitem> drop down box lets you choose a "
"dictionary for spell checking."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem oknu <guimenuitem>Slovar</guimenuitem> lahko izberete slovar za "
"preverjanje črkovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Sent-Mail Folder</guimenuitem> lets you specify where a local "
"copy of this message will be saved when you send it."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Mapa s poslanimi sporočili</guimenuitem> vam omogoča, da "
"določite, kam bo shranjena lokalna kopija tega sporočila, ko ga boste "
"poslali."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Mail Transport</guimenuitem> lets you select an outgoing mail "
"server."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Prenos pošte</guimenuitem> omogoča izbiro strežnika za odhodno "
"pošto."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The traditional From:, To:, and Subject: fields. (The Reply To: field will "
"appear only if you have specified an alternative <guilabel>Reply To</"
"guilabel> address on the <guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> tab in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure &kmail;...</"
"guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Accounts</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Identities</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog.)"
msgstr ""
"Tradicionalna polja Od:, Komu: in Zadeva:. (Polje Odgovori na: se prikaže "
"le, če ste določili alternativni naslov <guilabel>Odgovori</guilabel> na "
"zavihku <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel> v oknu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavitve &kmail;-a..."
"</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Računi</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Identitete</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>)"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Use Fixed Font</guimenuitem> toggles fixed width fonts on and "
"off."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Uporabi pisavo s fiksno širino</guimenuitem> vklopi ali izklopi "
"pisave s fiksno širino."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Snippets</guimenuitem> displays the snippets window, where you "
"may save frequently used bits of verbiage."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Izrezki</guimenuitem> prikaže okno izrezki, kamor lahko "
"shranite pogosto uporabljene delčke besedišča."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are a variety of shortcuts to help you select recipients. The "
"<guibutton>Select...</guibutton> button next to the <guilabel>To:</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>CC:</guilabel>, and <guilabel>BCC:</guilabel> fields "
"opens a list from &kaddressbook; so you can select one or more people who "
"should receive this message."
msgstr ""
"Pri izbiri prejemnikov si lahko pomagate z različnimi bližnjicami. Gumb "
"<guibutton>Izberi...</guibutton> poleg polj <guilabel>Za:</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>CC:</guilabel> in <guilabel>BCC:</guilabel> odpre seznam iz "
"&kaddressbook; tako lahko izberete eno ali več oseb, ki naj prejmejo to "
"sporočilo."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively, when you start typing an address in one of the <guilabel>To:</"
"guilabel>/<guilabel>CC:</guilabel>/<guilabel>BCC:</guilabel> fields, a popup "
"will appear that suggests similar recently used addresses and closely "
"matching addresses from &kaddressbook;; if you do not like this automatic "
"popup, you can disable it by clicking the &RMB; in the field where you're "
"typing, then choosing a different <guilabel>Text Completion &gt;</guilabel> "
"mode. You can also use this context menu to fine-tune the order in which "
"suggested completions appear (via <guilabel>Configure Completion...</"
"guilabel>)."
msgstr ""
"Druga možnost je, da se, ko začnete vnašati naslov v eno od polj "
"<guilabel>Za:</guilabel>/<guilabel>CC:</guilabel>/<guilabel>BCC:</guilabel>, "
"pojavi pojavno okno, ki predlaga podobne nedavno uporabljene naslove in zelo "
"podobne naslove iz &kaddressbook;; če vam to samodejno pojavno okno ni všeč, "
"ga lahko onemogočite s klikom na &RMB; v polju, v katerem vnašate naslov, in "
"nato izberete drug način <guilabel>Dopolnjevanja besedila &gt;</guilabel>. "
"Ta kontekstni meni lahko uporabite tudi za natančno nastavitev vrstnega "
"reda, v katerem se prikazujejo predlagana dopolnila (prek <guilabel>Nastavi "
"dopolnjevanje...</guilabel>)."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whenever you want to add more than one recipient in one of the fields, use a "
"comma to separate one address from the next one. You may have to specify "
"fully qualified addresses (&ie; <userinput>user@example.com</userinput>) "
"even for local users, depending on your system configuration."
msgstr ""
"Če želite v eno od polj dodati več kot enega prejemnika, uporabite vejico za "
"ločitev enega naslova od naslednjega. Morda boste morali navesti polno "
"kvalificirane naslove (&ie; <userinput>uporabnik@primer.com</userinput>) "
"tudi za lokalne uporabnike, odvisno od nastavitev vašega sistema."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are finished with your message, click the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"mail-send.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Send</guiicon> icon to "
"send the message now, or click the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-queue.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> Queue</guiicon> icon "
"to put the message in the outbox. If your message is not finished yet, "
"select <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save as Draft</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to save it for later editing. If you want to print "
"your message, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Print Preview</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to preview the "
"message, and <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to print it."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate s sporočilom, kliknite ikono "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"mail-send.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Pošlji</guiicon>, če "
"želite sporočilo poslati zdaj, ali kliknite ikono "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-queue.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> V vrsto</guiicon>, če "
"želite sporočilo odložiti v mapo odhajajoče. Če vaše sporočilo še ni "
"dokončano, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot osnutek</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da ga "
"shranite za poznejše urejanje. Če želite sporočilo natisniti, izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Predogled tiskanja</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> za predogled sporočila in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Natisni</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> za njegovo tiskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Later</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> lets you schedule your emails to be sent at a specific date and "
"time. Please see <ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_sendlater_agent\">Send Later "
"Agent</ulink> for details."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji kasneje</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> vam omogoča načrtovanje pošiljanja e-poštnih "
"sporočil na določen datum in ob določeni uri. Za podrobnosti glejte <ulink "
"url=\"help:/akonadi_sendlater_agent\">Posrednik za kasnejše pošiljanje</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kmail.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Message From "
"Template</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem><replaceable>My Super Template</"
"replaceable></guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Novo</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Sporočilo po predlogi</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem><replaceable>Moja super predloga</replaceable></guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Composing a new message from a template is useful when you have created a "
"masterpiece that you would like to use as a template for future new "
"messages. Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save as "
"Template</guimenuitem></menuchoice>; this will place your new template in "
"the <guilabel>templates</guilabel> folder. You can revise the template at "
"any time by selecting it from this folder. Double click on the template's "
"name (or press the shortcut key, <keycap>T</keycap>) to open it in a "
"composition window. You may also select the template via the <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> menu, as shown above."
msgstr ""
"Sestavljanje novega sporočila iz predloge je uporabno, kadar ste ustvarili "
"mojstrovino, ki jo želite uporabiti kot predlogo za prihodnja nova "
"sporočila. Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot predlogo</guimenuitem></menuchoice>; tako "
"boste novo predlogo postavili v mapo <guilabel>predloge</guilabel>. Predlogo "
"lahko kadar koli spremenite tako, da jo izberete iz te mape. Dvakrat "
"kliknite ime predloge (ali pritisnite tipkovno bližnjico <keycap>T</"
"keycap>), da jo odprete v oknu skladatelja. Predlogo lahko izberete tudi "
"prek menija <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu>, kot je prikazano zgoraj."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "Signing and Encrypting Messages"
msgstr "Podpisovanje in šifriranje sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to send an <link linkend=\"pgp-encrypt-your-messages"
"\">encrypted</link> or <link linkend=\"pgp-sign-your-messages\">digitally "
"signed</link> message, select the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-edit."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Sign</guiicon> "
"and / or <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-decrypt.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Encrypt</guiicon> icon in the toolbar. Use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Options</guimenuitem><guisubmenu>Cryptographic "
"Message Format &gt;</guisubmenu></menuchoice> dropdown list to select the "
"format used to encrypt the message. (The <guilabel>Options</guilabel> menu "
"also lets you sign / encrypt the message.) You may choose one of five "
"formatting options."
msgstr ""
"Če želite poslati <link linkend=\"pgp-encrypt-your-messages\">šifrirano</"
"link> ali <link linkend=\"pgp-sign-your-messages\">digitalno podpisano</"
"link> sporočilo, izberite ikono "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-edit."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Podpiši</guiicon> "
"in/ali <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-decrypt.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Šifriraj</guiicon> v orodni vrstici. S spustnim seznamom "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Možnosti</guimenuitem><guisubmenu>Oblika šifriranja "
"sporočil &gt;</guisubmenu></menuchoice> izberite obliko, ki se uporablja za "
"šifriranje sporočila. (V meniju <guilabel>Možnosti</guilabel> lahko "
"sporočilo tudi podpišete/šifrirate.) Izberete lahko eno od petih možnosti "
"oblikovanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Any</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Katerokoli</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; will use a format which is understood by all recipients of the "
"message. The preferred format for each recipient can be specified via <ulink "
"url=\"help:/kaddressbook\">&kaddressbook;</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; bo uporabil obliko, ki jo razumejo vsi prejemniki sporočila. "
"Prednostno obliko za vsakega prejemnika lahko določite prek <ulink url="
"\"help:/kaddressbook\">&kaddressbook;</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inline OpenPGP (deprecated)"
msgstr "Znotrajvrstični OpenPGP (opuščeno)"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This format is deprecated, but is supported for backward compatibility. If "
"you use this format then only the message text will be signed and/or "
"encrypted. <emphasis>Attachments will neither be signed nor encrypted.</"
"emphasis> &HTML; messages cannot be signed with this format. You should only "
"use this format when necessary, &ie; if you send messages to people who use "
"email clients that cannot handle the more advanced formats."
msgstr ""
"Ta oblika je zastarela, vendar je podprta zaradi združljivosti za nazaj. Če "
"uporabite to obliko, bo podpisano in/ali šifrirano samo besedilo sporočila. "
"<emphasis>Priponke ne bodo niti podpisane niti šifrirane.</emphasis> &HTML; "
"sporočil s to obliko ni mogoče podpisati. To obliko lahko uporabite le po "
"potrebi, če pošiljate sporočila ljudem, ki uporabljajo e-poštne odjemalce, "
"ki ne znajo uporabljati naprednejših oblik."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenPGP/&MIME;"
msgstr "OpenPGP/&MIME;"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This format is the successor to the inline OpenPGP format. If you use this "
"format then the message text and all attachments will be signed and/or "
"encrypted (at least by default). This is the recommended format if you use "
"OpenPGP encryption."
msgstr ""
"Ta format je naslednik vgrajenega formata OpenPGP. Če uporabite to obliko, "
"bodo besedilo sporočila in vse priloge podpisane in/ali šifrirane (vsaj "
"privzeto). To je priporočena oblika, če uporabljate šifriranje OpenPGP."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid "S/&MIME;"
msgstr "S/&MIME;"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This format is an alternative format to OpenPGP/&MIME;. If you use this "
"format then the message text and all attachments will be signed and/or "
"encrypted (at least by default). This format is mostly used by corporations. "
"It relies on an x.509 certificate, not a PGP / GPG key."
msgstr ""
"Ta format je alternativni format za OpenPGP/&MIME;. Če uporabite to obliko, "
"bodo besedilo sporočila in vse priloge podpisane in/ali šifrirane (vsaj "
"privzeto). To obliko večinoma uporabljajo podjetja. Temelji na potrdilu "
"x.509 in ne na ključu PGP/GPG."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid "S/&MIME; opaque"
msgstr "S/&MIME; opaque"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:513
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This format is a variant of the S/&MIME; format. Because it rolls the "
"message, any attachments, and the digital signature into a single &MIME; "
"object, it is cpu-intensive and should only be used if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Ta format je različica formata S/&MIME;. Ker združuje sporočilo, morebitne "
"priponke in digitalni podpis v en sam objekt &MIME;, je procesorsko potraten "
"in naj se uporablja le po potrebi."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating &HTML; Messages"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje &HTML; spročil"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that &HTML; messages are often regarded as an annoyance; therefore, you "
"should use &HTML; messages judiciously. In particular, you should never send "
"&HTML; messages to mailing list recipients unless &HTML; messages are "
"explicitly allowed."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da sporočila &HTML; pogosto veljajo za moteča, zato jih morate "
"uporabljati preudarno. Zlasti ne smete nikoli pošiljati sporočil &HTML; "
"prejemnikom poštnega seznama, razen če so sporočila &HTML; izrecno dovoljena."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create &HTML; messages, you must first enable the markup tools. To do "
"this, enable <guimenuitem>Rich Text Editing</guimenuitem> in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Options</guimenu></menuchoice> menu, or click on the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"preferences-"
"desktop-font.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Rich "
"Text</guiicon> icon on the &kmail; toolbar. An additional toolbar with "
"several formatting tools will appear. Via the &HTML; toolbar you can choose "
"standard text or bulleted / numbered lists. (Use the <guilabel>None "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"go-down.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guilabel> drop-down list at the "
"left edge of the toolbar to control the style of bulleted / numbered lists.) "
"You can also control the font family, the font size, the font style (bold, "
"italic, underlined, or strike-through) and the text / background color. And "
"you can specify the alignment of the text (left aligned, centered, right "
"aligned, or justified) and insert anchor tags (aka links), horizontal lines, "
"images, tables, and arbitrary &HTML; code (although support for some of the "
"more advanced &HTML; tags is still incomplete)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti sporočila &HTML;, morate najprej omogočiti orodja za "
"označevanje. To storite tako, da v meniju <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Možnosti</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> omogočite <guimenuitem>Urejanje z bogatim "
"besedilom</guimenuitem> ali kliknete ikono "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"preferences-"
"desktop-font.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Bogato "
"besedilo</guiicon> v orodni vrstici &kmail;-a. Pojavi se dodatna orodna "
"vrstica z več orodji za oblikovanje. V orodni vrstici &HTML;-ja lahko "
"izberete standardno besedilo ali označene / oštevilčene sezname. (Uporabite "
"<guilabel>Brez <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"go-down."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guilabel> spustni "
"seznam na levem robu orodne vrstice za nadzor sloga seznamov z odebeljenimi/"
"oštevilčenimi vrsticami.) Določite lahko tudi družino pisave, velikost "
"pisave, slog pisave (krepko, poševno, podčrtano ali prečrtano) in barvo "
"besedila / ozadja. Določite lahko tudi poravnavo besedila (leva poravnava, "
"sredinsko, desno poravnano ali poravnano) in vstavite oznake za sidra (t. i. "
"povezave), vodoravne črte, slike, tabele in poljubno kodo &HTML; (čeprav je "
"podpora za nekatere naprednejše oznake &HTML; še vedno nepopolna)."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Attachments"
msgstr "Dodajanje prilog"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can attach files to your message by using any of these methods."
msgstr "Pripenjanje datotek je mogoče z eno od naslednjih metod."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:553
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guisubmenu>Attach &gt;</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> dropdown list and ensuing dialog to choose a file;"
msgstr ""
"Za izbiro datoteke uporabite spustni seznam <menuchoice><guimenu>Pripni</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Pripni &gt;</guisubmenu></menuchoice> in posledično "
"pogovorno okno;"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-"
"attachment.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Attach "
"</guiicon> icon and select the file you wish to attach;"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ikono <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"mail-attachment.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Pripni </guiicon> in izberite datoteko, ki jo želite priložiti;"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Drag a file from the desktop or another folder into the composer window;"
msgstr "Povlecite datoteko iz namizja ali druge mape v okno skladatelja;"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Drag a message from &kmail;'s message list into the composer window – that "
"message will then be attached;"
msgstr ""
"Povleci sporočilo s seznama sporočil &kmail; v okno sestavljalnika sporočil "
"- to sporočilo bo nato priloženo;"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select one of the additional options in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Attach</"
"guimenu></menuchoice> menu; or"
msgstr ""
"Izberi eno izmed možnosti iz menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Priloži</guimenu></"
"menuchoice>; ali"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"document-open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Insert Text File ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Insert Recent Text File &gt;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"document-open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Vstavi besedilno datoteko ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Vstavi nedavno besedilno datoteko &gt;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once a file is attached to your message, it appears in the attachments pane "
"at the bottom of the composer window. You can use the &RMB; on each "
"attachment to <guimenuitem>View</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Open</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Reload</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>, or <guimenuitem>Remove</"
"guimenuitem> the attachment. (This context menu varies a little, depending "
"on the file type of the attachment.) Several options (Compress / Encrypt / "
"Sign / Suggest Automatic Display) may be toggled on or off for each file "
"attached to a message."
msgstr ""
"Ko je datoteka pripeta sporočilu se pojavi v pultu Priponke na koncu okna "
"skladatelja. Priponke lahko shranite, odstranite, pridobite več informacij "
"itd., če označite njeno ime in izberete <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Odstrani</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Shrani...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, ali <menuchoice><guimenuitem>lastnosti...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> iz menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Pripni</guimenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:589
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> item in the context menu to "
"open the <guilabel>Attachment Properties</guilabel> dialog. The first field "
"contains the attachment's &MIME; type. Just like the <guilabel>Name</"
"guilabel> field, it is automatically filled with an appropriate value. "
"Sometimes the &MIME; type may be wrong. You can then type in any &MIME; type "
"or choose from the list of common &MIME; types. You can also select an "
"encoding method for your file from the list of encoding options (normally, "
"the default value works fine). Check the <guilabel>Suggest automatic "
"display</guilabel> option if you want to suggest to the recipient the "
"automatic (inline) display of this attachment. Whether this works, or not, "
"depends on the recipient's email client, and on his settings."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite element <guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem> v kontekstnem meniju, "
"da odprete pogovorno okno <guilabel>Lastnosti priponke</guilabel>. Prvo "
"polje vsebuje vrsto &MIME; priponke. Tako kot polje <guilabel>Ime</guilabel> "
"se samodejno izpolni z ustrezno vrednostjo. Včasih je lahko vrsta &MIME; "
"napačna. Nato lahko vnesete katero koli vrsto &MIME; ali izberete s seznama "
"običajnih vrst &MIME;. S seznama možnosti kodiranja lahko izberete tudi "
"način kodiranja za svojo datoteko (običajno je privzeta vrednost ustrezna). "
"Označite možnost <guilabel>Predlagaj samodejni prikaz</guilabel>, če želite "
"prejemniku predlagati samodejni (vstavljeni) prikaz te priloge. Ali to "
"deluje ali ne, je odvisno od e-poštnega odjemalca prejemnika in njegovih "
"nastavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also attach public crypto keys to the message by choosing the "
"appropriate options in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Attach</guimenu></"
"menuchoice> menu. <application>GnuPG</application> keys and x.509 "
"certificates are (usually) handled as file attachments."
msgstr ""
"Sporočilu lahko priložite tudi javne šifrirne ključe, tako da izberete "
"ustrezne možnosti v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Pripni</guimenu></"
"menuchoice>. <application>Ključi GnuPG</application> in potrdila x.509 se "
"(običajno) obravnavajo kot priponke datotek."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checking the Spelling of your Message"
msgstr "Preverjanje Črkovanja Sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; can automatically check the spelling of your message and underline "
"unknown words in red. If there are too many unknown words, &kmail; will "
"disable its checking. To select the language used when checking, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dictionary</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. You can disable automatic spell checking in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Options</guimenu></menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; lahko samodejno preveri pravopis sporočila in podčrta neznane besede "
"z rdečo barvo. Če je neznanih besed preveč, &kmail; onemogoči preverjanje. "
"Če želite izbrati jezik, ki se uporablja pri preverjanju, izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Slovar</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. V meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu></menuchoice> "
"lahko onemogočite samodejno preverjanje črkovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to write mails in different languages, enable the "
"<guilabel>Dictionary</guilabel> drop down box with "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dictionary</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> from the menu. Using this drop down box allows you to change the "
"spell checker's language with one mouse click."
msgstr ""
"Če morate pisati pošto v različnih jezikih, omogočite spustno polje "
"<guilabel>Slovar</guilabel> z <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Slovar</guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz menija. S tem spustnim "
"oknom lahko z enim klikom miške spremenite jezik preverjanja črkovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:620
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To check the spelling of your message via a dialog, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spelling...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. &kmail; uses &sonnet; to check spelling; &sonnet; is the &kde; "
"frontend to the <application>Aspell</application>, <application>Hspell</"
"application>, <application>Enchant</application>, and <application>HUNSPELL</"
"application> spell checking programs. Note that you may need to configure "
"the spell checker using <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spellchecker...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preveriti črkovanje sporočila prek pogovornega okna, izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Črkovanje...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. &kmail; za preverjanje črkovanja uporablja "
"&sonnet; &sonnet; je &kde; pročelje za programe za preverjanje črkovanja "
"<application>Aspell</application>, <application>Hspell</application>, "
"<application>Enchant</application> in <application>HUNSPELL</application>. "
"Upoštevajte, da boste morda morali nastaviti preverjanje črkovanja z uporabo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preverjanje "
"črkovanja...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:633
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting Up the Text Snippets Tool"
msgstr "Nastavljanje orodja za koščke besedil"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When editing in the composer window you can insert frequently used bits of "
"text as snippets. To configure mail snippets, select <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Snippets</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"from the menubar. A new panel will appear on the right side of the composer "
"window."
msgstr ""
"Pri urejanju v oknu skladatelja lahko pogosto uporabljene dele besedila "
"vstavite kot izseke. Če želite konfigurirati odlomke pošte, v meniju "
"izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Koščki</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Na desni strani okna skladatelja se bo pojavila "
"nova plošča."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a new snippet to the Snippet Panel, right click on the panel, then "
"click <menuchoice><guimenu>Add Snippet</guimenu></menuchoice> in the context "
"menu. A snippet editor dialog will appear, in which new text can be added "
"and the snippet can be given a name. A <guilabel>Shortcut</guilabel> can "
"also be associated with the snippet. Snippets can be grouped together by "
"creating groups and adding snippets to a particular group. Use the &RMB; "
"context menu to add, edit, or remove snippets of text from the saved "
"collection."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati nov košček na ploščo s koščki, kliknite z desno tipko miške "
"na ploščo in nato v kontekstnem meniju kliknite <menuchoice><guimenu>Dodaj "
"košček</guimenu></menuchoice>. Pojavilo se bo pogovorno okno urejevalnika "
"izsekov, v katerem lahko dodate novo besedilo in izsek/košček poimenujete. Z "
"odlomkom je lahko povezana tudi <guilabel>Bližnjica</guilabel>. Utrinke "
"lahko združite v skupine z ustvarjanjem skupin in dodajanjem utrinkov v "
"določeno skupino. S kontekstnim menijem &RMB; lahko dodajate, urejate ali "
"odstranjujete odlomke besedila iz shranjene zbirke."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:644
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Snippets</guilabel> tool enables insertion of variable text in "
"predefined places any time you insert a snippet in a file. To do this, "
"<guilabel>Snippets</guilabel> provides its own variables mechanism. You can "
"insert variables in the snippet text itself by using separators ( $ ) to "
"enclose the variable names. For example: $variablename$, $invoicenumber$, "
"$weekno$."
msgstr ""
"Orodje <guilabel>Koščki</guilabel> omogoča vstavljanje spremenljivega "
"besedila na vnaprej določena mesta, kadar koli vstavite izsek v datoteko. V "
"ta namen <guilabel>Koščki</guilabel> zagotavlja svoj mehanizem spremenljivk. "
"Spremenljivke lahko vstavite v samo besedilo odlomka tako, da uporabite "
"ločila ( $ ), s katerimi zapišete imena spremenljivk. Na primer: "
"$variablename$, $invoicenumber$, $weekno$."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The variable separator can be changed to another character by changing "
"<varname>snippetDelimiter</varname> in the [SnippetPart] section in the Text "
"Snippet configuration file, which can be found at ~./config/kmailsnippetrc."
msgstr ""
"Spremenljivo ločilo lahko spremenite v drug znak tako, da spremenite "
"<varname>snippetDelimiter</varname> v razdelku [SnippetPart] v "
"konfiguracijski datoteki Text Snippet, ki jo najdete v ~./config/"
"kmailsnippetrc."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: using-kmail.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid "snippetDelimiter=$"
msgstr "snippetDelimiter=$"

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:657
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Built-in Translator"
msgstr "Uporaba vgrajenega prevajalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kmail; 2 composer provides a built-in translator that can be accessed "
"by selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Translator</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the menu bar. A new panel will appear at the "
"bottom of the composer window."
msgstr ""
"Skladatelj &kmail;-a 2 zagotavlja vgrajeni prevajalnik, do katerega lahko "
"dostopate z izbiro <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prevajalnik</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v menijski "
"vrstici. Na dnu okna skladatelja se prikaže nova plošča."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To translate a section of text, first enter the text you would like "
"translated in the box labeled <guilabel>Drag text that you want to translate."
"</guilabel>. Select the language in which it is written in the "
"<guilabel>From:</guilabel> drop down box. Select the language you would like "
"to translate to in the <guilabel>To:</guilabel> drop down box, then click "
"the <guibutton>Translate</guibutton> button. After being translated by "
"Google Translate, a free online service, your translated text will appear in "
"the next box. If you need to translate in the other direction you can just "
"click the <guibutton>Invert</guibutton> button. To clear all text, click the "
"<guibutton>Clear</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prevesti del besedila, najprej vnesite besedilo, ki ga želite "
"prevesti, v polje z oznako <guilabel>Potegnite besedilo, ki ga želite "
"prevesti.</guilabel>. V spustnem polju <guilabel>Iz:</guilabel> izberite "
"jezik, v katerem je napisan. V spustnem polju <guilabel>V:</guilabel> "
"izberite jezik, v katerega želite prevesti, nato kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Prevedi</guibutton>. Po prevajanju z Googlovim prevajalnikom, ki "
"je brezplačna spletna storitev, se prevedeno besedilo prikaže v naslednjem "
"polju. Če želite prevajati v drugo smer, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Zamenjaj</"
"guibutton>. Če želite počistiti vse besedilo, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Počisti</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:673
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message Folders"
msgstr "Mape s sporočili"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: using-kmail.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Folder Setup Example</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Primer nastavitve mape</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: using-kmail.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Folder Setup Example</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Primer nastavitve mape</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmail;'s default folders."
msgstr "&kmail;-ove privzete mape."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Message Folders are used to organize your email messages. When you first "
"start &kmail; the <quote>Local Folders</quote> containing <guilabel>inbox</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>outbox</guilabel>, <guilabel>sent-mail</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>trash</guilabel>, <guilabel>drafts</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>templates</guilabel> folders are created. Each of these folders "
"has a special function."
msgstr ""
"Z mapami za sporočila urejate e-poštna sporočila. Ob prvem zagonu programa "
"&kmail; se ustvarijo <quote>Mestne mape</quote>, ki vsebujejo mape "
"<guilabel>vhodna pošta</guilabel>, <guilabel>izhodna pošta</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>poslana pošta</guilabel>, <guilabel>smeti</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>osnutki</guilabel> in <guilabel>predloge</guilabel>. Vsaka od teh "
"map ima posebno funkcijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid "inbox:"
msgstr "prejeta pošta:"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Where &kmail; by default puts your new messages when you tell it to check "
"your mail."
msgstr ""
"Sem &kmail; privzeto spravi novo prejeta sporočila, ku mu naročite, naj "
"preveri pošto."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:699
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&IMAP; accounts will not use this inbox. The &IMAP; inbox is located on the "
"&IMAP; server."
msgstr ""
"&IMAP; računi ne bodo uporabljali tega predala. Prejeto sporočilo &IMAP; se "
"nahaja v strežniku &IMAP;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "outbox:"
msgstr "izhodna pošta:"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Where messages are put while they are waiting to be delivered. You must not "
"just drag and drop messages here to send them; use the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-send.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Send</guiicon> icon "
"in the composer window instead."
msgstr ""
"Kamor se shranjujejo sporočila, ki čakajo na dostavo. Za pošiljanje sporočil "
"tukaj ne smete samo povleči in spustiti; namesto tega uporabite ikono "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-send.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> pošlji</guiicon> v "
"oknu skladatelja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid "sent-mail:"
msgstr "odposlana pošta:"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid "By default, a copy of every message you send is saved in this folder."
msgstr "Privzeto vsebuje kopije že poslanih sporočil (vseh, ki jih pošljete)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:717
#, no-c-format
msgid "trash:"
msgstr "smeti:"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, all messages that you have designated as trash are moved into "
"this folder."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto se vsa sporočila, ki ste jih označili kot smeti, premaknejo v to "
"mapo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid "drafts:"
msgstr "osnutki:"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Contains messages you started to write but then saved to this folder with "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save as Draft</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Vsebuje sporočila, ki ste jih začeli pisati, vendar ste jih nato shranili v "
"to mapo s funkcijo <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot osnutek</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:728
#, no-c-format
msgid "templates:"
msgstr "predloge:"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This folder holds your templates created via <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Save as Template</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the "
"composer window. Please see <link linkend=\"new-compose-from-templates\">New "
"Composer Templates</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"V tej mapi so shranjene vaše predloge, ustvarjene prek "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot predlogo</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz okna skladatelja. Za podrobnosti glejte <link "
"linkend=\"new-compose-from-templates\">Nove predloge skladatelja</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating and Using Folders"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje in uporabljanje map"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Organize your emails (&eg; mailing lists, bills and receipts, &etc;) by "
"creating new folders. To create a new folder, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Add Folder...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or <guimenuitem>Add Folder...</guimenuitem> from "
"the &RMB; context menu. A dialog will pop up. Enter the name of the new "
"folder in the text box. You can fully customize each folder (&ie; views, "
"replies, &etc;) by selecting the folder you wish to modify in the folders "
"pane and then choosing <guimenuitem>Folder Properties</guimenuitem> from the "
"&RMB; context menu. See <link linkend=\"folders-properties-window"
"\">Properties of Folders</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Z ustvarjanjem novih map uredite e-pošto (&eg; poštne sezname, račune in "
"potrdila &etc;). Če želite ustvariti novo mapo, izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodaj mapo...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali <guimenuitem>Dodaj mapo...</guimenuitem> iz &RMB; "
"kontekstnega menija. Pojavilo se bo pogovorno okno. V besedilno polje "
"vnesite ime nove mape. Vsako mapo lahko v celoti prilagodite (&ie; poglede, "
"odgovore, &etc;) tako, da v podoknu map izberete mapo, ki jo želite "
"spremeniti, in nato v &RMB; kontekstnem meniju izberete "
"<guimenuitem>Lastnosti mape</guimenuitem>. Za podrobnosti glejte <link "
"linkend=\"folders-properties-window\">Lastnosti map</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move messages from one folder into another, select the message(s) you "
"want to move and press the <keycap>M</keycap> key or select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Move Message To... &gt;</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. A list of folders will appear; select the folder "
"into which you wish to move the message from that list. Messages can also be "
"moved by dragging them from the Message list to a folder in the Folder list, "
"or by using a context menu invoked with the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Če želite premakniti sporočila iz ene mape v drugo, izberite sporočila, ki "
"jih želite premakniti, in pritisnite tipko <keycap>M</keycap> ali izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Premakni sporočilo v... "
"&gt;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prikazal se bo seznam map; s seznama "
"izberite mapo, v katero želite premakniti sporočilo. Sporočila lahko "
"premaknete tudi tako, da jih s seznama sporočil povlečete v mapo na seznamu "
"map ali uporabite kontekstni meni, ki ga prikličete z &RMB;.Za premik "
"sporočil iz ene mape v drugo ga (jih) označi ter pritistni tipko <keycap>M</"
"keycap> oz. izberi <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prestavi v</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. V prikazanem "
"seznamu map označite mapo, v katero želite sporočilo prestaviti. Enako lahko "
"dosežete tudi z povlečenjem sporočil(a) iz Seznama sporočil v mapo v pult "
"Mape."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have folders that are frequently accessed, you can add them to your "
"favorite folders pane (above the list of folders). Add them with the &RMB; "
"context menu option <guimenuitem>Add to Favorite Folders</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če imate mape, do katerih pogosto dostopate, jih lahko dodate v podokno "
"priljubljenih map (nad seznamom map). Dodajte jih z možnostjo &RMB; "
"kontekstnega menija <guimenuitem>Dodaj v priljubljene mape</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:753
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can create a virtual folder with search parameters by going to "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find Messages...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or by using keyboard shortcut <keycap>S</keycap>. "
"Enter your search parameters into the dialog. Name your search with the "
"<guilabel>Search folder name:</guilabel> textbox, &eg; <replaceable>emails "
"with the word Blog</replaceable>. Click the <guibutton>Search</guibutton> "
"button. Now select the <guibutton>Open Search Folder</guibutton> button. A "
"results folder will open, positioned at the bottom of the Folder pane. (By "
"default, each new search is named \"Last Search\". You can save particular "
"search parameters by assigning a special name as described above.)"
msgstr ""
"Navidezno mapo s parametri iskanja lahko ustvarite tako, da odprete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči sporočila...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali uporabite bližnjico na tipkovnici <keycap>S</"
"keycap>. V pogovorno okno vnesite parametre iskanja. Iskanje poimenujte z "
"besedilnim poljem <guilabel>Naziv iskalne mape:</guilabel>, &eg; "
"<replaceable>sporočila z besedo Blog</replaceable>. Kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Poišči</guibutton>. Zdaj izberite gumb <guibutton>Odpri iskalno "
"mapo</guibutton>. Odprla se bo mapa z rezultati na dnu podokna z mapami. "
"(Privzeto je vsako novo iskanje poimenovano \"Zadnje iskanje\". Določene "
"parametre iskanja lahko shranite tako, da jim dodelite posebno ime, kot je "
"opisano zgoraj.)"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:759
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creating filters to automatically move messages to specified folders is a "
"great way to organize messages by mailing list, sender, subject &etc; Please "
"see <link linkend=\"filters\">Filters</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjanje filtrov za samodejno premikanje sporočil v določene mape je "
"odličen način za organizacijo sporočil po poštnem seznamu, pošiljatelju, "
"predmetu in podobno; Za podrobnosti glejte <link linkend=\"filters\">Filtri</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you receive emails from a trusted source (&eg; a Blog you signed up for) "
"that is formatted in &HTML; and you would like to enable &HTML; view for "
"those emails only, you can create a new folder, set up a <link linkend="
"\"filters\">filter</link> to place all email from the Blog in the new "
"folder, select the folder, and then choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Folder</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Message Default Format &gt;</guimenuitem> "
"<guimenuitem>Prefer &HTML; to Plain Text</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če prejemate e-poštna sporočila iz zaupanja vrednega vira (npr. Bloga, na "
"katerega ste se prijavili), ki so oblikovana v &HTML; in želite omogočiti "
"prikaz &HTML; samo za ta e-poštna sporočila, lahko ustvarite novo mapo, "
"nastavite <link linkend=\"filters\">filter</link>, da se vsa e-poštna "
"sporočila iz Bloga prenesejo v novo mapo, izberete mapo in nato izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Privzet format sporočila &gt;"
"</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Prednjači &HTML; pred navadnim besedilom</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some common folder actions are"
msgstr "Nekatera pogosta dejanja map so"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kmail.docbook:772
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Move All Messages to Trash</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Premakni vsa sporočila v koš</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Move</action> all the messages in the selected folder to the trash "
"folder."
msgstr "<action>Premakni</action> vsa sporočila v izbrani mapi v mapo smeti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kmail.docbook:777
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Archive Folder</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mapa arhiva</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Create an archive</action> of the folder. See <link linkend=\"folder-"
"archive\">Archive Folder</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"<action>Izdelajte arhiv</action> mape. Za podrobnosti glejte <link linkend="
"\"folder-archive\">Mapa arhiva</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kmail.docbook:782
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Delete Folder</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbriši mapo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Remove a folder</action> with all its messages and sub-folders."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odstranitev mape</action> z vsemi njenimi sporočili in podmapami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kmail.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Remove Duplicate Messages</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odstrani podvojena sporočila</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Search</action> the currently selected folder for duplicates and "
"<action>delete</action> them."
msgstr ""
"<action>Poiščite</action> trenutno izbrano mapo za podvojenimi datotekami in "
"jih <action>odstrani</action>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:796
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder Properties"
msgstr "Lastnosti mape"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: using-kmail.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Folder Properties Example</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Primer lastnosti mape</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: using-kmail.docbook:804
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Folder Properties Example</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Primer lastnosti mape</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:807
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Folder Properties Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno lastnosti mape"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:812
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Properties of Folder</guilabel> dialog lets you specify its "
"properties. Note that some properties are only available for the folders you "
"create and not for default folders like <guilabel>inbox</guilabel> &etc; The "
"six default folders cannot be renamed."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Lastnosti mape</guilabel> lahko določite njene "
"lastnosti. Upoštevajte, da so nekatere lastnosti na voljo samo za mape, ki "
"jih ustvarite, in ne za privzete mape, kot so <guilabel>prejeta pošta</"
"guilabel> in druge; šestih privzetih map ni mogoče preimenovati."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:816
#, no-c-format
msgid "General tab"
msgstr "Zavihek splošno"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to rename a folder, change the entry in the <guilabel>Name:</"
"guilabel> field."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preimenovati mapo, spremenite besedilo v polju <guilabel>Ime:</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Act on new/unread mail in this folder</guilabel> is enabled by "
"default on new folders. It enables notifications about new mail that arrives "
"in the folder. Uncheck this option on folders like SPAM and trash for which "
"you do not desire notifications."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Učinek na novo/neprebrano pošto v tej mapi</guilabel> je privzeto "
"omogočen za nove mape. Omogoča obvestila o novi pošti, ki prispe v mapo. "
"Odkljukajte to možnost pri mapah, kot sta SPAM in smeti, za katere ne želite "
"prejemati obvestil."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Keep replies in this folder</guilabel> if you want replies "
"to these messages to be stored in this folder rather than in the default "
"configured sent-mail folder."
msgstr ""
"Označite možnost <guilabel>Odgovore ohrani v tej mapi</guilabel>, če želite, "
"da so odgovori na ta sporočila shranjeni v tej mapi in ne v privzeto "
"nastavljeni mapi za poslano pošto."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:823
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Hide this folder in the folder selection dialog</guilabel> "
"if you do not want this folder to be shown in folder selection dialogs, such "
"as the <guimenuitem>Jump to Folder</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Move "
"Message to</guimenuitem> dialogs."
msgstr ""
"Označite možnost <guilabel>Skrij to mapo v pogovornem oknu za izbiro mape</"
"guilabel>, če ne želite, da je ta mapa prikazana v pogovornih oknih za "
"izbiro mape, kot sta <guimenuitem>Pojdi v mapo</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>Premakni sporočilo v</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"New folders use the default identity. If you wish to associate a folder with "
"a different identity, uncheck <guilabel>Use default identity</guilabel> and "
"select a different one from the <guilabel>Sender identity</guilabel> drop "
"down menu. See <link linkend=\"configure-identity\">Identities "
"configuration</link> for information on Identities. Replies to messages that "
"were sent directly to you will still default to the message's <quote>To</"
"quote> address if a matching identity is found."
msgstr ""
"Nove mape uporabljajo privzeto identiteto. Če želite mapo povezati z drugo "
"identiteto, odstranite potrditev <guilabel>Uporabljaj privzeto identieto</"
"guilabel> in v spustnem meniju <guilabel>Indentiteta pošiljatelja</guilabel> "
"izberite drugo identiteto. Za informacije o identitetah glejte <link linkend="
"\"configure-identity\">Nastavitve identitet</link>. Odgovori na sporočila, "
"ki so bila poslana neposredno vam, bodo še vedno privzeti na naslov "
"<quote>Za</quote> sporočila, če bo najdena ustrezna identiteta."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:840
#, no-c-format
msgid "View tab"
msgstr "Zavihek pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:841
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Use custom icons</guilabel> option lets you choose icons that "
"are different from the defaults in the folder list."
msgstr ""
"Z možnostjo <guilabel>Uporabljaj ikone po meri</guilabel> lahko izberete "
"ikone, ki se razlikujejo od privzetih na seznamu map."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the <guilabel>Show column</guilabel> drop down list you can set the "
"visible columns in the header pane to Default, Sender, or Receiver. This may "
"be useful if you use a custom folder to save some of your own sent messages."
msgstr ""
"S pomočjo spustnega seznama <guilabel>Pokaži stolpec</guilabel> lahko "
"nastavite vidne stolpce v podoknu z glavo na Privzeto, Pošiljatelj ali "
"Prejemnik. To je lahko koristno, če uporabljate mapo po meri za shranjevanje "
"nekaterih lastnih poslanih sporočil."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:844
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Message List</guilabel> section you can select and "
"configure an <guilabel>Aggregation</guilabel> and <guilabel>Theme</guilabel> "
"for this folder that differs from the default configured in &kmail;s "
"settings. For more details see the <link linkend=\"configure-appearance-"
"message-list\"> Message List</link> tab on the <guilabel>Appearance</"
"guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Seznam sporočil</guilabel> lahko izberete in nastavite "
"<guilabel>Združevanje</guilabel> in <guilabel>Temo</guilabel> za to mapo, ki "
"se razlikuje od privzetih nastavitev v &kmail;u. Za več podrobnosti glejte "
"zavihek <link linkend=\"configure-appearance-message-list\"> Seznam "
"sporočil</link> na strani <guilabel>Videz</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:847
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Message Default Format</guilabel> section lets you choose "
"between plain and &HTML; displays for messages in this folder."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Privzeta oblika sporočila</guilabel> lahko izbirate med "
"navadnim in &HTML; prikazom za sporočila v tej mapi."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:851
#, no-c-format
msgid "Retrieval tab"
msgstr "Zavihek pridobivanje"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:852
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have an account that does not receive much mail and you don't want "
"&kmail; to query the server too often, you can uncheck <guilabel>Use options "
"from parent folder or account</guilabel> to set a longer interval in the "
"<guilabel>Automatically synchronize after:</guilabel> spin box."
msgstr ""
"Če imate račun, ki ne prejema veliko pošte, in ne želite, da bi &kmail; "
"prepogosto poizvedoval po strežniku, lahko odkljukate možnost "
"<guilabel>Uporabljaj nastavitve nadrejene mape oz. računa</guilabel> in v "
"polju <guilabel>Samodejno uskladi po:</guilabel> nastavite daljši interval."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:854
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <guilabel>Retrieval Options</guilabel> you can change the "
"<guilabel>Always retrieve full messages</guilabel> option to "
"<guilabel>Retrieve message bodies on demand</guilabel> if you have a slow "
"connection. You can also set how long the message will be retained locally "
"via the spin box."
msgstr ""
"V možnosti <guilabel>Možnosti pridobivanja</guilabel> lahko možnost "
"<guilabel>Vedno pridobivaj celotna sporočila</guilabel> spremenite v "
"<guilabel>Pridobivaj telesa sporočil na zahtevo</guilabel>, če imate počasno "
"povezavo. V polju za vrtenje lahko tudi nastavite, koliko časa bo sporočilo "
"shranjeno lokalno."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:860
#, no-c-format
msgid "Templates tab"
msgstr "Zavihek predloge"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:861
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this tab you can define folder-specific templates for your custom "
"folders. For more details see the <link linkend=\"configure-composer-"
"standard-templates\"> Standard Templates</link> tab on the "
"<guilabel>Composer</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"V tem zavihku lahko za mape po meri določite predloge za posamezne mape. Za "
"več podrobnosti glejte zavihek <link linkend=\"configure-composer-standard-"
"templates\"> Standardne predloge</link> na strani <guilabel>Skladatelj</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:868
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expiry tab"
msgstr "Zavihek zastaranja"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set up automatic cleanup or deletion of emails. Check the box if you "
"would like to automatically expire read or unread messages respectively. Set "
"the number of days in the spin box. If you do not want to delete the "
"messages permanently, you can assign a folder to keep them in via the "
"<guilabel>Move expired messages to:</guilabel> text box / folder selection "
"dialog. Once you have reviewed the messages and want to delete them "
"permanently, you can go to the folder expiry options of the folder you chose "
"to move them to and set the option <guilabel>Delete expired messages "
"permanently</guilabel>, then click the <guibutton>Save Settings and Expire "
"Now</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite lahko samodejno čiščenje ali brisanje e-poštnih sporočil. Označite "
"polje, če želite, da se samodejno izteče veljavnost prebranih oziroma "
"neprebranih sporočil. V vrtilnem polju nastavite število dni. Če sporočil ne "
"želite trajno izbrisati, lahko prek besedilnega polja <guilabel>Premakni "
"pretečena sporočila v:</guilabel> ali pogovornega okna za izbiro mape "
"določite mapo, v kateri bodo ostala. Ko sporočila pregledate in jih želite "
"trajno izbrisati, pojdite v možnosti za potek veljavnosti mape, v katero ste "
"jih želeli premakniti, in nastavite možnost <guilabel>Trajno izbriši "
"sporočila, ki jim je potekla veljavnost</guilabel>, nato pa kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Shrani nastavitve in preteči zdaj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:876
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Messages that are deleted cannot be restored, so be careful with this "
"setting."
msgstr ""
"Izbrisanih sporočil ni mogoče ponovno pridobiti, zato bodite s to "
"nastavitvijo previdni."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:881
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mailing List tab"
msgstr "Zavihek seznam pošiljanja"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:883
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are going to use the folder for a mailing list open the "
"<guilabel>Mailing List Folder Properties</guilabel> dialog with "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Folder</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mailing List Management</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> from the menu. Then you should check "
"<guilabel>Folder holds a mailing list</guilabel> to associate this folder "
"with the mailing list. Next you should click on <guilabel>Detect "
"Automatically</guilabel>. &kmail; will then try to guess some information "
"about the mailing list from the currently selected message. If &kmail; could "
"not determine some addresses then you can add the missing information "
"manually. To do this first select the <guilabel>Address type</guilabel> for "
"which you want to add an address. You can choose among five options."
msgstr ""
"Če boste mapo uporabili za poštni seznam, odprite pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Lastnosti mape poštnega seznama</guilabel> z izbiro "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Mapa</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Upravljanje poštnega "
"seznama</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> iz menija. Nato morate preveriti možnost "
"<guilabel>Mapa vsebuje poštni seznam</guilabel>, da to mapo povežete s "
"poštnim seznamom. Nato kliknite <guilabel>Zaznaj samodejno</guilabel>. "
"&kmail; bo nato poskušal uganiti nekaj informacij o poštnem seznamu iz "
"trenutno izbranega sporočila. Če &kmail; ni mogel določiti nekaterih "
"naslovov, lahko manjkajoče informacije dodate ročno. Za to najprej izberite "
"<guilabel>Tip naslova</guilabel>, za katerega želite dodati naslov. Izbirate "
"lahko med petimi možnostmi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:896
#, no-c-format
msgid "Post to List"
msgstr "Pošta v seznam"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:898
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This address is used for sending messages to the mailing list. This is "
"usually an email address."
msgstr ""
"Naslov se uporablja za pošiljanje sporočil na poštni seznam. To je ponavadi "
"e-naslov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:901
#, no-c-format
msgid "Subscribe to List"
msgstr "Naroči se na seznam"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This address is used for subscribing to the mailing list. This can be an "
"email address or the address of a web page."
msgstr ""
"Ta naslov se uporablja za prijavo na poštni seznam. To je lahko e-poštni "
"naslov ali naslov spletne strani."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unsubscribe From List"
msgstr "Prekini naročnino na seznam"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:907
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This address is used for unsubscribing from the mailing list. This can be an "
"email address or the address of a web page."
msgstr ""
"Ta naslov se uporablja za odjavo s poštnega seznama. To je lahko e-poštni "
"naslov ali naslov spletne strani."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:910
#, no-c-format
msgid "List Archives"
msgstr "Arhiv seznama"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:911
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the address of the archive of the mailing list. This is usually the "
"address of a web page."
msgstr ""
"To je naslov arhiva poštnega seznama. To je običajno naslov spletne strani."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:914
#, no-c-format
msgid "List Help"
msgstr "Pomoč za seznam"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This address is used for requesting help for this mailing list. This is "
"usually an email address."
msgstr ""
"Ta naslov se uporablja za prošnjo za pomoč za ta poštni seznam. Običajno je "
"to e-poštni naslov."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After selecting the appropriate <guilabel>Address type</guilabel>, enter the "
"email address or the address of the web page and then click on "
"<guilabel>Add</guilabel>. With <guilabel>Remove</guilabel> you can remove "
"addresses."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete ustrezno vrsto <guilabel>Različica naslova</guilabel>, vnesite e-"
"poštni naslov ali naslov spletne strani in nato kliknite <guilabel>Dodaj</"
"guilabel>. S funkcijo <guilabel>Odstrani</guilabel> lahko odstranite naslove."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:925
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When all the addresses have been added, you can execute an action, &eg; go "
"to the list archives, by selecting the appropriate <guilabel>Address type</"
"guilabel> and then clicking on <guilabel>Invoke Handler</guilabel>. If there "
"is an email address and an address of a web page for the desired action, you "
"will have to select the <guilabel>Preferred handler</guilabel> prior to "
"clicking on <guilabel>Invoke Handler</guilabel>. Select <guilabel>KMail</"
"guilabel> if you want to send a message to the email address and select "
"<guilabel>Browser</guilabel> if you want to go to the web page."
msgstr ""
"Ko so dodani vsi naslovi, lahko izvedete dejanje, &eg; pojdite na seznam "
"arhivov, tako da izberete ustrezen <guilabel>Tip naslova</guilabel> in nato "
"kliknete <guilabel>Pokliči ročnik</guilabel>. Če sta na voljo e-poštni "
"naslov in naslov spletne strani za želeno dejanje, boste morali izbrati "
"<guilabel>Prednostni prednostni ročnik</guilabel>, preden kliknete na "
"<guilabel>Pokliči ročnik</guilabel>. Izberite <guilabel>KMail</guilabel>, če "
"želite poslati sporočilo na e-poštni naslov, in <guilabel>Brskalnik</"
"guilabel>, če želite obiskati spletno stran."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:935
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also send a new message to the mailing list via "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Message to Mailing-"
"List...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (instead of <guilabel>Invoke Handler</"
"guilabel>)."
msgstr ""
"Novo sporočilo lahko pošljete na poštni seznam tudi prek "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo sporočilo na "
"poštni seznam...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (namesto <guilabel>Pokliči "
"ročnik</guilabel>)."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:941
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut tab"
msgstr "Zavihek bližnjica"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can define a keyboard shortcut to access the folder."
msgstr "Definirate lahko tipkovno bližnjico, s katero dostopate do mape."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:946
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maintenance tab"
msgstr "Zavihek vzdržavanje"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:947
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab shows an overview about the folder type and its size, the number of "
"read and unread messages in the folder and allows you to enable text "
"indexing."
msgstr ""
"Ta zavihek prikazuje pregled vrste mape in njene velikosti, število "
"prebranih in neprebranih sporočil v mapi ter omogoča omogočanje indeksiranja "
"besedila."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:953
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quota tab (&IMAP; only)"
msgstr "Zavihek kvote (samo &IMAP;)"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab will show you how much space has been allocated to your &IMAP; "
"account by the server, and also how much of the allocated space you are "
"currently using."
msgstr ""
"V tem zavihku je prikazano, koliko prostora je strežnik dodelil vašemu "
"računu &IMAP; in koliko dodeljenega prostora trenutno uporabljate."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:961
#, no-c-format
msgid "Access Control tab (&IMAP; only)"
msgstr "Zavihek nadzora dostopa (samo &IMAP;)"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can manage the access control lists (&acl;s) of &IMAP; folders."
msgstr "Tu lahko upravljate sezname za nadzor dostopa (&acl;i) map &IMAP;."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:963
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &IMAP; server must have user level &acl; configured and enabled for this "
"tab to be visible."
msgstr ""
"Da je ta zavihek viden, mora biti v strežniku &IMAP; nastavljena in "
"omogočena uporabniška raven &acl;."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:964
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The currently active &acl; is shown in the list. It consists of pairs of "
"<guilabel>User Id</guilabel>s and the <guilabel>Permissions</guilabel> "
"granted to users identified by that <guilabel>User Id</guilabel>. <footnote> "
"<para>Note that a single <guilabel>User Id</guilabel> might refer to more "
"than one user. Depending on the &IMAP; server and its configuration, there "
"may be User Ids that correspond to groups of users, anonymous users, or any "
"user. Consult the manual of your specific &IMAP; server implementation for "
"more information.</para> </footnote> &acl;s are settable per-folder."
msgstr ""
"Na seznamu je prikazan trenutno aktivni &acl;. Sestavljen je iz parov "
"<guilabel>Uporabniški Id</guilabel> in <guilabel>Dovoljenja</guilabel>, ki "
"so dodeljena uporabnikom, identificiranim s tem <guilabel>Uporabniškim Id-"
"jem</guilabel>. <footnote> <para>Pazite, da se lahko en "
"<guilabel>Uporabniški Id</guilabel> nanaša na več kot enega uporabnika. "
"Odvisno od strežnika &IMAP; in njegove konfiguracije lahko obstajajo "
"identifikacijske številke uporabnikov, ki ustrezajo skupinam uporabnikov, "
"anonimnim uporabnikom ali kateremu koli uporabniku. Za več informacij se "
"obrnite na priročnik za izvajanje strežnika &IMAP;.</para> </footnote> &acl;"
"i so nastavljivi za posamezno mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:971
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As with everything else when using <emphasis>disconnected &IMAP;</emphasis>, "
"you need to sync with the server for the changes to be transferred to the "
"server."
msgstr ""
"Tako kot pri vsem drugem, ko uporabljate <emphasis>odklopljen &IMAP;</"
"emphasis>, se morate sinhronizirati s strežnikom, da se spremembe prenesejo "
"v strežnik."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&IMAP; &acl;s define a lot of fine-grained permissions that you can grant or "
"deny other users. For the sake of clarity, &kmail; will present them as the "
"following five categories that you can choose from (see <xref linkend="
"\"table-acl-summary\"/> for the details if you already know &IMAP; &acl;s)."
msgstr ""
"&IMAP; &acl;i določajo veliko podrobnih dovoljenj, ki jih lahko dodelite ali "
"zavrnete drugim uporabnikom. Zaradi jasnosti jih bomo predstavili v "
"naslednjih petih kategorijah, med katerimi lahko izbirate (za podrobnosti "
"glejte <xref linkend=\"table-acl-summary\"/>, če že poznate &IMAP; &acl;e)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid "None"
msgstr "Brez"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:980
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Grants the users identified by <guilabel>User Id</guilabel> no rights at "
"all. This is also the default for users not explicitly (or implicitly, as a "
"group) listed in the &acl;. These users will not see this folder in the list "
"of &IMAP; folders presented to them by their mail clients."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnikom, ki jih identificira <guilabel>Uporabniški Id</guilabel>, ne "
"podeli nobenih pravic. To je tudi privzeto za uporabnike, ki niso izrecno "
"(ali implicitno, kot skupina) navedeni v &acl;. Ti uporabniki te mape ne "
"bodo videli na seznamu map &IMAP;, ki jim ga prikažejo njihovi poštni "
"odjemalci."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:985
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Read</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Branje</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:987
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Grants the users identified by <guilabel>User Id</guilabel> reading rights "
"for this folder. This also includes the ability for their mail clients to "
"mark mails as read and store this information on the server."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnikom, identificiranim z <guilabel>Uporabniškim Id-jem</guilabel>, "
"podeli pravice branja za to mapo. To vključuje tudi možnost, da njihovi "
"poštni odjemalci označijo pošto kot prebrano in to informacijo shranijo v "
"strežnik."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:990
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every user has their own list of read mail, so none of your unread mails "
"will suddenly be marked as read just because someone else has already read "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Vsak uporabnik ima svoj seznam prebrane pošte, zato nobena vaša neprebrana "
"pošta ne bo nenadoma označena kot prebrana samo zato, ker jo je nekdo drug "
"že prebral."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:994
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These users will see this folder in the list of &IMAP; folders presented to "
"them by their mail clients."
msgstr ""
"Ti uporabniki bodo to mapo videli na seznamu map &IMAP;, ki jim ga prikažejo "
"njihovi poštni odjemalci."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:995
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this to create a shared folder that others can read, but not modify."
msgstr ""
"S to možnostjo ustvarite mapo v skupni rabi, ki jo lahko drugi berejo, "
"vendar ne morejo spreminjati."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:997
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you were the editor of a company's news letter, you could create a folder "
"for the purpose of distributing the news letter, grant everyone reading "
"rights, and save the letter to this folder instead of sending it out by "
"email to a catch-all address."
msgstr ""
"Če ste urednik novic podjetja, lahko ustvarite mapo za distribucijo novic, "
"vsem podelite pravico do branja in pismo shranite v to mapo, namesto da bi "
"ga poslali po e-pošti na skupni naslov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1003
#, no-c-format
msgid "Append"
msgstr "Dodajanje"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1005
#, no-c-format
msgid "(also known as <guilabel>Post</guilabel>)"
msgstr "(znano tudi kot <guilabel>Objavljanje</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Grants the users identified by <guilabel>User Id</guilabel> reading (see "
"above) and posting rights for this folder."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnikom, identificiranim z <guilabel>Uporabniškim Id-jem</guilabel>, "
"podeli pravice branja (glej zgoraj) in objavljanja za to mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this to create a shared folder that others can read and post messages "
"to, but cannot otherwise modify."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite jo za ustvarjanje mape v skupni rabi, v kateri lahko drugi berejo "
"in objavljajo sporočila, vendar je ne morejo drugače spreminjati."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1009
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you wanted to create a company-wide discussion forum, instead of using a "
"web-based form or a separate company-private usenet server, you could create "
"a bunch of folders (one per topic), and grant everyone reading and posting "
"rights. Instead of posting to an &nntp; server or writing their messages "
"into a web form, people would just write emails and store them in the folder "
"suiting the topic of the message."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti forum za razpravo v celotnem podjetju, lahko namesto "
"spletnega obrazca ali ločenega zasebnega strežnika Usenet v podjetju "
"ustvarite več map (po eno na temo) in vsem podelite pravice za branje in "
"objavljanje. Namesto da bi sporočila pošiljali na strežnik &nntp; ali jih "
"pisali v spletni obrazec, bi ljudje pisali elektronska sporočila in jih "
"shranjevali v mapo, ki bi ustrezala temi sporočila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid "Write"
msgstr "Pisanje"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1017
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Grants the users identified by <guilabel>User Id</guilabel> reading, posting "
"(see above), and writing rights for this folder."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnikom, identificiranim z <guilabel>Uporabniškim Id-jem</guilabel>, "
"podeli pravice branja, objavljanja (glej zgoraj) in pisanja za to mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1018
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The right to write to a folder includes deleting of messages, creating "
"subfolders, and storing other attributes than read/unread on the server "
"(&eg; answered)."
msgstr ""
"Pravica do pisanja v mapo vključuje brisanje sporočil, ustvarjanje podmap in "
"shranjevanje drugih lastnosti v strežniku, razen prebrano/neprebrano (&eg; "
"odgovorjeno)."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1020
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this to create a shared folder that everyone has (almost, see <xref "
"linkend=\"folders-properties-acl-all\"/>) the same rights for."
msgstr ""
"S tem ustvarite mapo v skupni rabi, za katero imajo vsi (skoraj, glejte "
"<xref linkend=\"folders-properties-acl-all\"/>) enake pravice."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1022
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <xref linkend=\"folders-properties-acl-append\"/> example, you could "
"assign write rights to a group of people acting as moderators, who would "
"then be able to remove off-topic posts, and create sub-topic folders for "
"high-traffic folders."
msgstr ""
"V primeru <xref linkend=\"folders-properties-acl-append\"/> bi lahko "
"dodelili pravice za pisanje skupini ljudi, ki bi delovali kot moderatorji, "
"ki bi lahko odstranili objave, ki niso povezane s temo, in ustvarili podmape "
"za mape z veliko prometa."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1027
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>All</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Vse</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1029
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Grants the users identified by <guilabel>User Id</guilabel> reading, "
"posting, writing (see above), as well as administration rights, &ie; the "
"right to modify the &acl; of this folder."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnikom, identificiranim z <guilabel>Uporabniškim Id-jem</guilabel>, "
"podeli pravice branja, objavljanja, pisanja (glej zgoraj) in tudi pravice "
"upravljanja, &ie; pravico do spreminjanja &acl; te mape."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1031
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is the default set of rights for the owner of a folder."
msgstr "To so privzete pravice za lastnika mape."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1034
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"summarizes the &IMAP; &acl; rights associated with each permission level."
msgstr "povzame pravice&IMAP; &acl;, povezane z vsako stopnjo dovoljenja."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid "&acl; Rights Summary"
msgstr "&acl; povzetek pravic"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1040
#, no-c-format
msgid "&acl; right"
msgstr "&acl; desno"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lookup"
msgstr "Iskanje"

#. Tag: entry
