msgstr "Upravljaj"

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message Filters"
msgstr "Filtri sporočil"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: using-kmail.docbook:1134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Filter Dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno za filtre</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: using-kmail.docbook:1140
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Filter Dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za filtre</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1143
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Filter Creation Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za ustvarjanje filtrov"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After using &kmail; for a while, you may find that you have trouble sorting "
"out the new messages in your inbox when they arrive. Filters allow you to "
"automatically perform certain actions on incoming messages and to manually "
"perform actions on selected messages in a folder."
msgstr ""
"Ko boste nekaj časa uporabljali storitev &kmail;, boste morda ugotovili, da "
"imate težave z razvrščanjem novih prejetih sporočil. Filtri omogočajo "
"samodejno izvajanje določenih dejanj za dohodna sporočila in ročno izvajanje "
"dejanj za izbrana sporočila v mapi."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Filters consist of filter criteria, whose rules are used to determine "
"whether this filter should be applied to a given message, and a list of "
"filter actions, which describe what is to be done with, or to, the message "
"if the search pattern matches."
msgstr ""
"Filtri so sestavljeni iz meril za filtriranje, katerih pravila se "
"uporabljajo za določitev, ali naj se filter uporabi za določeno sporočilo, "
"in seznama dejanj filtriranja, ki opisujejo, kaj naj se stori s sporočilom "
"ali z njim, če se vzorec iskanja ujema."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Filters are considered one after the other, starting with the first filter "
"in the list. The first one whose pattern matches the given message is "
"applied; you can request that the remaining filters also be processed, but "
"the default is to stop processing at the first matching filter."
msgstr ""
"Filtri se obravnavajo drug za drugim, začenši s prvim filtrom na seznamu. "
"Uporabi se prvi filter, katerega vzorec se ujema z danim sporočilom; "
"zahtevate lahko, da se obdelajo tudi preostali filtri, vendar se obdelava "
"privzeto ustavi pri prvem filtru, ki se ujema."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Usually, filters are used on incoming messages, but they can also be applied "
"to sent messages or to an arbitrary message or group of messages. To "
"selectively filter messages, select the messages you want to filter in the "
"message list and either type <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>J</"
"keycap> </keycombo> or select <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Apply Filter</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This will apply the "
"filters (the ones that have been marked for manual filtering in the <link "
"linkend=\"filter-dialog\">advanced filter dialog</link>) to those messages."
msgstr ""
"Običajno se filtri uporabljajo za dohodna sporočila, lahko pa jih uporabite "
"tudi za poslana sporočila ali poljubno sporočilo ali skupino sporočil. Če "
"želite selektivno filtrirati sporočila, izberite sporočila, ki jih želite "
"filtrirati, na seznamu sporočil in vnesite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>J</keycap> </keycombo> ali izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uporabi filter</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. To bo "
"uporabilo filtre (tiste, ki so bili označeni za ročno filtriranje v <link "
"linkend=\"filter-dialog\">naprednem pogovornem oknu za filtriranje</link>) "
"za ta sporočila."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fast Filter Creation"
msgstr "Hitro ustvarjanje filtrov"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two methods for creating a filter; the quick method is to use "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Create Filter</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and select a criterion from the submenu. This will "
"open the filter dialog and present you with a new filter which has the first "
"rule of the search pattern and the first action (as <guilabel>Move into "
"Folder</guilabel>) preset. In most cases, all you have to do is select the "
"folder where the message should be moved, but you can, of course, edit the "
"filter as you like."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje filtra obstajata dve metodi; hitra metoda je uporaba "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ustvari filter</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in izbira merila v podmeniju. To bo odprlo "
"pogovorno okno filtra in prikazalo nov filter, ki ima prednastavljeno prvo "
"pravilo vzorca iskanja in prvo dejanje (kot <guilabel>Premakni v mapo</"
"guilabel>). V večini primerov je treba le izbrati mapo, v katero naj bi se "
"sporočilo premaknilo, seveda pa lahko filter poljubno urejate."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When creating a filter on mailing list messages, this method will try to "
"find a criterion that uniquely identifies messages from the list. If it "
"succeeds, the guessed name of the list is presented in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Create Filter</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Filter on Mailing-List...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"menu entry."
msgstr ""
"Pri ustvarjanju filtra za sporočila poštnega seznama bo ta metoda poskušala "
"najti pravilo, ki edinstveno identificira sporočila s seznama. Če uspe, je "
"ugibano ime seznama predstavljeno v vnosu menija "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Izdelaj filter</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Filter na poštnem seznamu...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The second method is to manually construct a filter from scratch by calling "
"the filter dialog through <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Filters...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The "
"filter dialog is described in detail in the following subsection."
msgstr ""
"Drugi način ustvarjanja filtrov je s priklicom okna "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavi Filtre...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Okno urejevalnika filtrov je opisano v "
"nadaljevanju."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1204
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The Filter Dialog</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pogovorno okno filtra</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1207
#, no-c-format
msgid "This dialog allows you to manage and edit your list of filters."
msgstr "To pogovorno okno omogoča upravljanje in urejanje seznama filtrov."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reach it either via <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Create Filter</guisubmenu></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Filters...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Do njega lahko pridete prek <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Izdelaj filter</guisubmenu></menuchoice> ali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavi filtre...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The dialog is divided into three main sections on the <guilabel>General</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> tabs."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno je razdeljeno na tri glavne razdelke na zavihkih "
"<guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> in <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available Filters"
msgstr "Filtri na voljo"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains the list of filters and some action buttons to modify "
"the filters, namely: create new filters; move them up or down the list; copy "
"one of them; delete them; or rename them. If you select a filter from the "
"list, its properties are shown in the right-hand half of the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ta skupina vsebuje seznam filtrov in nekaj gumbov za spreminjanje filtrov, "
"in sicer: ustvarjanje novih filtrov, premikanje po seznamu navzgor ali "
"navzdol, kopiranje enega od njih, brisanje ali preimenovanje. Če s seznama "
"izberete filter, so njegove lastnosti prikazane v desnem delu pogovornega "
"okna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter Criteria"
msgstr "Kriterij filtriranja"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this group you can edit the pattern that messages must match before the "
"filter is applied to them. You can select whether all of the defined rules "
"must match, or whether a single match is enough. See <link linkend=\"filter-"
"criteria\">Search Patterns</link> below for a detailed description of each "
"search rule type."
msgstr ""
"V tej skupini lahko urejate vzorec, ki mu morajo sporočila ustrezati, preden "
"se zanje uporabi filter. Izberete lahko, ali se morajo ujemati vsa "
"opredeljena pravila ali pa zadostuje eno samo ujemanje. Za podroben opis "
"vsake vrste pravila iskanja glejte <link linkend=\"filter-criteria\">Išči "
"vzorce</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can click on <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> to get an "
"additional (initially empty) rule if you want to define more complex "
"patterns, and on <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> to remove the "
"selected rule. <guibutton>Clear</guibutton> clears the pattern, &ie;, it "
"removes all but one rule from the screen and resets it."
msgstr ""
"Če želite določiti bolj zapletene vzorce, lahko kliknete na <guibutton>&nbsp;"
"&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton>, da dobite dodatno (sprva prazno) pravilo, in na "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton>, da odstranite izbrano pravilo. "
"<guibutton>Počisti</guibutton> izbriše vzorec, &ie; odstrani vsa pravila "
"razen enega z zaslona in ga ponastavi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter Actions"
msgstr "Dejanja filtra"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this group you can edit the list of actions that are applied to all "
"messages that match the defined filter criteria. See <link linkend=\"filter-"
"action\">Filter Actions</link> below for a detailed description of each "
"action type."
msgstr ""
"V tej skupini lahko urejate seznam ukrepov, ki se uporabijo za vsa "
"sporočila, ki ustrezajo opredeljenim merilom za filtriranje. Za podroben "
"opis vsake vrste akcije glejte <link linkend=\"filter-action\">Dejanja "
"filtra</link> spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can click on <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> to get a new, "
"empty action (if you want to define more than one action), and on "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> to remove the selected action. "
"<guibutton>Clear</guibutton> clears the list, &ie; it removes all but one "
"action and resets that one."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> lahko dobite novo, "
"prazno dejanje (če želite določiti več kot eno dejanje), s klikom na "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> pa odstranite izbrano dejanje. "
"<guibutton>Počisti</guibutton> počisti seznam, &ie; odstrani vsa dejanja "
"razen enega in ga ponastavi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Options"
msgstr "Napredne možnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this group you can define a few advanced options that allow you to fine "
"tune your filtering."
msgstr ""
"V tej skupini lahko določite nekaj naprednih možnosti, s katerimi lahko "
"natančno prilagodite filtriranje."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the first row of check boxes, you can toggle when the filter is "
"applied: the <guilabel>Apply this filter to incoming messages</guilabel> "
"option means that the filter is applied to messages when you receive them "
"(&ie; on <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-"
"receive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Check Mail</"
"guiicon>). The filter can be applied to all messages, to all but online IMAP "
"accounts, or to particular incoming email accounts."
msgstr ""
"S prvo vrstico potrditvenih polj lahko preklopite, kdaj se filter uporabi: "
"možnost <guilabel>Uporabi ta filter za dohodna sporočila</guilabel> pomeni, "
"da se filter uporabi za sporočila, ko jih prejmete (&ie; na "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-receive."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Preverite pošto</"
"guiicon>). Filter lahko uporabite za vsa sporočila, za vse račune IMAP razen "
"spletnih ali za določene račune dohodne e-pošte."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Apply this filter to sent messages</guilabel> option means "
"that the filter is applied to messages when you send them, and the "
"<guilabel>Apply this filter on manual filtering</guilabel> option controls "
"whether to apply this filter when filtering is specifically selected (&ie; "
"via <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Apply Filters</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>.)"
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Uporabi ta filter za poslana sporočila</guilabel> pomeni, "
"da se filter uporabi za sporočila, ko jih pošljete, možnost "
"<guilabel>Uporabi ta filter pri ročnem filtriranju</guilabel> pa določa, ali "
"se ta filter uporabi, ko je filtriranje posebej izbrano (&ie; prek "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uporabi filtre</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>)"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Apply this filter to sent messages</guilabel> is checked the "
"filter will be triggered <emphasis>after</emphasis> the message is sent and "
"it will only affect the local copy of the message. If the recipient's copy "
"also needs to be modified, please use <guilabel>Apply this filter before "
"sending messages</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno polje <guilabel>Uporabi ta filter za poslana sporočila</"
"guilabel>, se filter sproži <emphasis>po</emphasis>poslanem sporočilu in "
"vpliva samo na lokalno kopijo sporočila. Če je treba spremeniti tudi kopijo "
"prejemnika, uporabite <guilabel>Pred pošiljanjem sporočil uporabite ta "
"filter</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>If this filter matches, stop processing here</guilabel> check "
"box controls whether or not the filters after the current filter will be "
"processed when the current filter matches."
msgstr ""
"S potrditvenim poljem <guilabel>Če se ta filter ujema, prenehaj z obdelavo</"
"guilabel> določite, ali bodo filtri za trenutnim filtrom obdelani, ko se "
"trenutni filter ujema."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Add this filter to the Apply Filter menu</guilabel> check "
"box is selected, this filter will be inserted in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Apply Filter</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> submenu. You can then apply this single filter to "
"a message or a set of messages. If you select this option, you may "
"optionally select a keyboard shortcut and insert a special icon to invoke "
"this filter from the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno potrditveno polje <guilabel>Dodaj ta filter v meni Uporabi "
"filter</guilabel>, bo ta filter vstavljen v podmenu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uporabi filter</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ta enojni filter lahko nato uporabite za "
"sporočilo ali niz sporočil. Če izberete to možnost, lahko po želji izberete "
"bližnjico na tipkovnici in vstavite posebno ikono, da ta filter prikličete "
"iz orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another way of applying filters is to use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Apply Filters</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu option, "
"which applies <emphasis>all</emphasis> the filters – one after another – "
"until they are all used or one of the filters that matches specifies the "
"<guilabel>If this filter matches, stop processing here</guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"Drug način uporabe filtrov je uporaba možnosti menija "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uporaba filtrov</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, ki uporabi <emphasis>vse</emphasis> filtre - "
"enega za drugim - dokler se vsi ne uporabijo ali dokler eden od filtrov, ki "
"ustreza, ne določi možnosti <guilabel>Če se ta filter ujema, prenehaj z "
"obdelavo.</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Filters are automatically named unless you explicitly rename them using the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Rename...</"
"guibutton> button. The dialog assumes that it should continue auto-naming "
"the filter as long as the filter name starts with <quote>&lt;</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Filtri so samodejno poimenovani, razen če jih izrecno preimenujete z gumbom "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Preimenuj...</"
"guibutton>. Pogovorno okno predpostavlja, da mora nadaljevati s samodejnim "
"poimenovanjem filtra, dokler se ime filtra začne z <quote>&lt;</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you apply filter changes, via <guibutton>OK</guibutton> or "
"<guibutton>Apply</guibutton>, only the valid filters are actually copied to "
"the internal filter manager."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabite spremembe filtrov prek <guibutton>OK</guibutton> ali "
"<guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton>, se v notranji upravitelj filtrov dejansko "
"kopirajo samo veljavni filtri."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similarly, empty rules and actions are removed from the pattern and action "
"lists, respectively, before the filter is saved."
msgstr ""
"Podobno se pred shranjevanjem filtra s seznama vzorcev in seznama dejanj "
"odstranijo prazna pravila in dejanja."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Patterns"
msgstr "Išči vzorce"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most common use of filters is to filter on the sender of messages. This "
"can be done by choosing <guilabel>From</guilabel>. A good bet for a mailing "
"list would be <guilabel>All Recipients</guilabel>, but there are other "
"criteria a filter can search for (note that all patterns are interpreted "
"case-insensitively)."
msgstr ""
"Najpogostejša uporaba filtrov je filtriranje pošiljatelja sporočil. To lahko "
"storite z izbiro <guilabel>Od</guilabel>. Dobra izbira za poštni seznam je "
"<guilabel>Vsi prejemniki</guilabel>, vendar lahko filter išče tudi po drugih "
"merilih (upoštevajte, da so vsa iskanja vzorcev občutljiva na velikost črk)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1338 using-kmail.docbook:1447
#, no-c-format
msgid "Complete Message"
msgstr "Celotno sporočilo"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searches the whole message (&ie; headers, body and attachments, if any)."
msgstr ""
"Preišče celotno sporočilo (&ie; glave, telo in priponke, če obstajajo)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Body of Message"
msgstr "Telo sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searches the body of the message (&ie; the whole message except the headers)."
msgstr "Preišče telo sporočila (&ie; celotno sporočilo razen glave)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1351
#, no-c-format
msgid "Anywhere in Headers"
msgstr "Kjerkoli v glavah"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searches all the headers in the message."
msgstr "Preišče vse glave v sporočilu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1357
#, no-c-format
msgid "All Recipients"
msgstr "Vsi prejemniki"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searches the <quote>To</quote> and <quote>CC</quote> header fields of the "
"message."
msgstr ""
"Preišče polji <quote>Za</quote> in <quote>CC</quote> v glavi sporočila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1363
#, no-c-format
msgid "Size in Bytes"
msgstr "Velikost v bajtih"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets upper or lower bounds on the message's size."
msgstr "Nastavi zgornjo in spodnjo mejo velikosti sporočila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1369
#, no-c-format
msgid "Age in Days"
msgstr "Starost v dnevih"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1371
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets upper or lower bounds on the message's age."
msgstr "Nastavi zgornjo in spodnjo mejo starosti sporočila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1375 using-kmail.docbook:1498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message Status"
msgstr "Status sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets restrictions on the status of the message (Important / Read / Unread / "
"&etc; see <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mark Message "
"&gt;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi omejitve statusa sporočila (Pomembno / Prebrano / Neprebrano / &etc; "
"glejte <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Oznake sporočila "
"&gt;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1382
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message Tag"
msgstr "Oznaka sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checks for tagged messages. See <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Mark Message &gt;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Preveri za označena sporočila. Glejte <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Označi sporočilo &gt;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1388
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encrypted"
msgstr "Šifrirano"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1390
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checks for encrypted messages."
msgstr "Preveri za šifrirana sporočila."

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:1394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any other value (<guilabel>From</guilabel>, <guilabel>To</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Date</guilabel>, &etc;)"
msgstr ""
"Katera koli druga vrednost (<guilabel>Od</guilabel>, <guilabel>do</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>datum</guilabel>, &etc;)"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1396
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searches the header field with that name."
msgstr "Preišče polje glave z navedenim imenom."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1401
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list of possible rules depends on what you selected in the first drop "
"down box. The available rules are:"
msgstr ""
"Seznam možnih pravil je odvisen od tega, kaj ste izbrali v prvem spustnem "
"polju. Na voljo so naslednja pravila:"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1408
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rule"
msgstr "Pravilo"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1409
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available for"
msgstr "Na voljo za"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1410
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1415
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>contains</guilabel>/<guilabel>does not contain</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>vsebuje</guilabel>/<guilabel>ne vsebuje</guilabel>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1416 using-kmail.docbook:1440
#, no-c-format
msgid "all textual search items"
msgstr "vsi besedilni elementi iskanja"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches if the searched item contains (or does not contain) the given text."
msgstr ""
"Ugotavlja, ali iskani element vsebuje (ali ne vsebuje) podano besedilo."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1421
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>equals</guilabel>/<guilabel>does not equal</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>je enako</guilabel>/<guilabel>ni enako</guilabel>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1422 using-kmail.docbook:1428 using-kmail.docbook:1434
#, no-c-format
msgid "most textual search items"
msgstr "večina besedilnih elementov iskanja"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches if the searched item is equal to (or not equal to) the given text."
msgstr "Ujema se, če je iskani element enak (ali ni enak) danemu besedilu."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>starts with</guilabel>/<guilabel>does not start with</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>začne z</guilabel>/<guilabel>ne začne z</guilabel>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches if the searched item begins with (or does not begin with) the given "
"text."
msgstr ""
"Ujema se, če se iskani element začne z danim besedilom (ali se ne začne z "
"njim)."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1433
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>ends with</guilabel>/<guilabel>does not end with</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>se konča z</guilabel>/<guilabel>se ne konča z</guilabel>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1435
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches if the searched item ends with (or does not end with) the given text."
msgstr ""
"Ujema se, če se iskani element konča z danim besedilom (ali se ne konča z "
"njim)."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>matches regular expr.</guilabel>/<guilabel>does not match reg. "
"expr.</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>ustreza regularnemu izrazu</guilabel>/<guilabel>ne ustreza "
"regularnemu izrazu</guilabel>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches if a part of the searched item matches the given regular expression "
"(or does not match it). If the regular expression editor is installed then "
"you can edit the regular expression by clicking on the <guilabel>Edit...</"
"guilabel> button."
msgstr ""
"Ujema se, če se del iskanega elementa ujema z danim regularnim izrazom (ali "
"se ne ujema). Če je nameščen urejevalnik regularnih izrazov, lahko regularni "
"izraz uredite s klikom na gumb <guilabel>Urejanje...</guilabel>."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>has an attachment</guilabel>/<guilabel>has no attachment</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>ima priponko</guilabel>/<guilabel> nima priponke</guilabel>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches if the message has an attachment (or does not have an attachment)."
msgstr "Ujema se, če ima sporočilo priponko (ali je nima)."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1467
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>is equal to</guilabel>/<guilabel>is not equal to</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>je enako</guilabel>/<guilabel>ni enako</guilabel>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1468 using-kmail.docbook:1474 using-kmail.docbook:1480
#: using-kmail.docbook:1486 using-kmail.docbook:1492
#, no-c-format
msgid "numerical search items"
msgstr "številčni elementi iskanja"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches if the value of the search item is equal to (or not equal to) the "
"specified value."
msgstr ""
"Ujema se, če je vrednost iskanega elementa enaka (ali ni enaka) določeni "
"vrednosti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1473
#, no-c-format
msgid "is less than"
msgstr "je manj kot"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches if the value of the search item is less than the specified value."
msgstr ""
"Ujema se, če je vrednost iskanega elementa manjša od določene vrednosti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1479
#, no-c-format
msgid "is greater than"
msgstr "je več kot"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches if the value of the search item is greater than the specified value."
msgstr ""
"Ujema se, če je vrednost iskanega elementa večja od določene vrednosti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1485
#, no-c-format
msgid "is less than or equal to"
msgstr "je manj ali enako kot"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1487
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches if the value of the search item is less than or equal to the "
"specified value."
msgstr ""
"Ujema se, če je vrednost iskanega elementa manjša ali enaka določeni "
"vrednosti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1491
#, no-c-format
msgid "is greater than or equal to"
msgstr "je večje ali enako kot"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches if the value of the search item is greater than or equal to the "
"specified value."
msgstr ""
"Ujema se, če je vrednost iskanega elementa večja ali enaka določeni "
"vrednosti."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1497
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>is</guilabel>/<guilabel>is not</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>je</guilabel>/<guilabel>ni</guilabel>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1499
#, no-c-format
msgid "Matches if the message has (or does not have) the specified status."
msgstr "Ujema se, če ima (ali nima) sporočilo določeno stanje."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>is after</guilabel>/<guilabel>is before or equal to</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>je za</guilabel>/<guilabel>je pred ali enako</guilabel>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1503 using-kmail.docbook:1508
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Date</guilabel> header"
msgstr "<guilabel>Datum</guilabel> v glavi"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1504
#, no-c-format
msgid "Matches if the message was sent after (not after) the specified date."
msgstr "Ustreza, če je bilo sporočilo poslano po (ali ne po) navedenem datumu."

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>is before</guilabel>/<guilabel>is after or equal to</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>je pred</guilabel>/<guilabel>je za ali enako</guilabel>"

#. Tag: entry
#: using-kmail.docbook:1509
#, no-c-format
msgid "Matches if the message was sent before (not before) the specified date."
msgstr ""
"Ujema se, če je bilo sporočilo poslano pred (ali ne pred) določenim datumom."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1518
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter Action"
msgstr "Dejanja filtra"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most common use of filters is to divert some incoming messages to "
"particular folders; this can be done by choosing <guilabel>Move into Folder</"
"guilabel>. Here is a list of all possible actions."
msgstr ""
"Najpogostejša uporaba filtrov je preusmeritev nekaterih prejetih sporočil v "
"določene mape; to lahko storite tako, da izberete <guilabel>Premakni v mapo</"
"guilabel>. Tukaj je seznam vseh možnih dejanj."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1526
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move Into Folder"
msgstr "Premakni v mapo"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will move the message into another folder, and remove it from its "
"current folder."
msgstr ""
"Sporočilo se bo premaknilo v drugo mapo in odstranilo iz trenutne mape."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1534
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy Into Folder"
msgstr "Kopiraj v mapo"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will copy the message to another folder, and leave the message in the "
"current folder."
msgstr ""
"Sporočilo se kopira v drugo mapo, hkrati pa sporočilo ostane v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1542
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set Identity To"
msgstr "Nastavi identiteto na"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will set the identity that will be used when you reply to this message."
msgstr ""
"S tem določite identiteto, ki bo uporabljena, ko boste odgovorili na to "
"sporočilo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1549
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mark As"
msgstr "Označi kot"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to mark the message as read or important (flagged), but also "
"as forwarded, replied, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Tako lahko sporočilo označite kot prebrano ali pomembno (z zastavico), pa "
"tudi kot posredovano, odgovorjeno &etc;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1556
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Tag"
msgstr "Dodaj označbo"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will add a tag to the message. You may choose from a list of all the "
"tags that have been defined."
msgstr ""
"Sporočilu bo dodana oznaka. Izbirate lahko s seznama vseh opredeljenih oznak."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1563
#, no-c-format
msgid "Send Fake MDN"
msgstr "Pošlji lažno obvestilo o usodi"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1565
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will send a faked message disposition notification (&ie; a read "
"receipt) to the sender of the message."
msgstr ""
"To bo pošiljatelju sporočila poslalo lažno obvestilo o usodi sporočila (&ie; "
"potrdilo o branju)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set Transport To"
msgstr "Nastavi prenos na"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will set the method of transport (&eg; &SMTP;) that will be used when "
"you reply to the message. You may choose from a list of all your outgoing "
"email accounts."
msgstr ""
"S tem nastavite način prenosa (&eg; &SMTP;), ki bo uporabljen pri "
"odgovarjanju na sporočilo. Izberete lahko s seznama vseh računov za odhodno "
"e-pošto."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1577
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set Reply-To To"
msgstr "»Odgovori-na« nastavi na"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will modify the <guilabel>Reply-To</guilabel> field of this message. "
"This can be useful for mailing lists that automatically set a Reply-To "
"address you do not wish to use."
msgstr ""
"To bo spremenilo polje <guilabel>Odgovori-na</guilabel> tega sporočila. To "
"je lahko koristno za poštne sezname, ki samodejno nastavijo naslov za "
"odgovor na sporočilo, ki ga ne želite uporabljati."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1584
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forward To"
msgstr "Posreduj"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will forward the message inline (&ie; as if you selected "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Inline...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>) to another "
"email address. You may select a custom forwarding template if such a "
"template has been defined. If &kaddressbook; is installed, you may choose "
"the <quote>Forward To</quote> address from a pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"To bo sporočilo posredovalo znotraj vrstice (&ie; kot če bi izbrali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Posreduj</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Znotraj vrstice...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>) na "
"drug e-poštni naslov. Izberete lahko predlogo za posredovanje po meri, če je "
"takšna predloga opredeljena. Če je nameščen &kaddressbook;, lahko v pojavnem "
"oknu izberete naslov <quote>Posreduj</quote>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1592
#, no-c-format
msgid "Redirect To"
msgstr "Preusmeri do"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will redirect the message as-is to another email address. If "
"&kaddressbook; is installed, you may choose the <quote>Redirect To</quote> "
"address from a pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"To bo sporočilo preusmerilo na drug e-poštni naslov. Če je nameščen "
"&kaddressbook;, lahko v pojavnem oknu izberete naslov <quote>Preusmeri na</"
"quote>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1598
#, no-c-format
msgid "Confirm Delivery"
msgstr "Potrdi dostavo"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will return a message to the sender that verifies successful delivery of "
"their message, if the sender requested that."
msgstr ""
"Pošiljatelju vrne sporočilo, ki potrjuje uspešno dostavo njegovega "
"sporočila, če je pošiljatelj to zahteval."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action allows you to select who will get delivery receipts from you. "
"Though you can globally enable the sending of delivery confirmations in the "
"<guilabel>Configure &kmail;...</guilabel> dialog (<link linkend=\"configure-"
"security\"><guilabel>Security</guilabel> page</link>) we do not recommend "
"that you send them to everyone, since this makes tracking of spam messages "
"very easy for the spammers."
msgstr ""
"S tem dejanjem lahko izberete, kdo bo od vas prejemal potrdila o dostavi. "
"Čeprav lahko globalno omogočite pošiljanje potrdil o dostavi v pogovornem "
"oknu <guilabel>Nastavi &kmail;...</guilabel> (<link linkend=\"configure-"
"security\">stran<guilabel>Varnost</guilabel></link>), ne priporočamo, da jih "
"pošiljate vsem, saj s tem pošiljateljem neželene pošte zelo olajšate "
"sledenje sporočilom."

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:1610
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Execute Command</guilabel> (for advanced users only)"
msgstr "<guilabel>Izvedi ukaz</guilabel> (samo za napredne uporabnike)"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will execute a program, but will not modify the message. Specify the "
"full path to the program you want to execute; &kmail; will then wait until "
"the program returns. If you do not want &kmail; to wait, append '&amp;' to "
"the command. You can feed the segments of the message into the program one "
"by one: <symbol>&percnt;0</symbol>, <symbol>&percnt;1</symbol>, &etc; stand "
"for files representing the message segments. For common messages, "
"<symbol>&percnt;0</symbol> is the plain text message, <symbol>&percnt;1</"
"symbol> the first attachment and so on. Additionally, the whole message is "
"fed into the program's <acronym>stdin</acronym>; and every occurrence of "
"<symbol>&percnt;{foo}</symbol> is replaced by the content of the foo header. "
"If you need to identify the message via its storage location in the Akonadi "
"database, you can use the %{itemid} or %{itemurl} placeholders to achieve "
"that."
msgstr ""
"To bo izvedlo program, vendar ne bo spremenilo sporočila. Navedite celotno "
"pot do programa, ki ga želite izvesti; &kmail; bo nato počakal, da se "
"program vrne. Če ne želite, da &kmail; čaka, ukazu dodajte '&amp;'. Segmente "
"sporočila lahko v program vnesete enega za drugim: <symbol>&percnt;0</"
"symbol>, <symbol>&percnt;1</symbol>, &etc; pomenijo datoteke, ki "
"predstavljajo segmente sporočila. Pri običajnih sporočilih je "
"<symbol>&percnt;0</symbol> navadno besedilno sporočilo, <symbol>&percnt;1</"
"symbol> prva priponka in tako naprej. Poleg tega se celotno sporočilo "
"prenese v <acronym>stdin</acronym> programa; vsak pojav <symbol>&percnt;{foo}"
"</symbol> pa se nadomesti z vsebino glave foo. Če morate sporočilo "
"identificirati prek lokacije shranjevanja v zbirki podatkov Akonadi, lahko "
"za to uporabite nadomestna imena %{itemid} ali %{itemurl}."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1629
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This currently only works if the message has <emphasis>at least one</"
"emphasis> attachment. No, not even <symbol>&percnt;0</symbol> will work in "
"the general case!"
msgstr ""
"To trenutno deluje le, če ima sporočilo <emphasis>vsaj eno</emphasis> "
"priponko. Ne, niti <symbol>&percnt;0</symbol> ne bo delovala v splošnem "
"primeru!"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter arbitrarily-complex shell commands here, since &kmail; uses a "
"sub shell to execute the command line; therefore, even this command will "
"work (within its limits): <userinput><command>uudecode</command> <option>-o</"
"option> <parameter>$(mktemp kmail-uudecoded.XXXXXX)</parameter> &amp;&amp; "
"<command>echo</command> <parameter>$'\\a'</parameter></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko vnesete poljubno zapletene ukaze lupine, saj &kmail; za izvajanje "
"ukazne vrstice uporablja podluplino; zato bo deloval tudi ta ukaz (v okviru "
"njegovih omejitev): <userinput><command>uudecode</command> <option>-o</"
"option> <parameter>$(mktemp kmail-uudecoded.XXXXXX)</parameter> &amp;&amp; "
"<command>echo</command> <parameter>$'\\a'</parameter></userinput>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1644
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pipe Through"
msgstr "Pošlji skozi"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1646
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will feed the message to a program: if the program returns output, the "
"entire message (including the headers) will be replaced with this output; if "
"the program does not return output or exits with a return code other than 0 "
"(indicating an error occurred), the message will not change. Specify the "
"full path to the program. The same substitutions (<symbol>&percnt;n</"
"symbol>, <symbol>&percnt;{foo}</symbol> as with <guilabel>Execute Command</"
"guilabel> may be performed on the command line."
msgstr ""
"To bo sporočilo posredovalo programu: če program vrne izhod, bo celotno "
"sporočilo (vključno z naslovi) nadomeščeno s tem izhodom; če program ne vrne "
"izhoda ali se konča s kodo vrnitve, ki ni 0 (kar pomeni napako), se "
"sporočilo ne bo spremenilo. Navedite celotno pot do programa. V ukazni "
"vrstici se lahko izvedejo enake zamenjave (<symbol>&percnt;n</symbol>, "
"<symbol>&percnt;{foo}</symbol> kot pri <guilabel>Izvedi ukaz</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1654
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Both the Anti-Spam Wizard and the Anti-Virus Wizard use the <quote>Pipe "
"Through</quote> action to check for spam / malware. The commonly available "
"anti-spam and anti-virus programs return the message, and insert an extra "
"header record, if spam (or a virus) is detected."
msgstr ""
"Tako čarovnik za preprečevanje neželene pošte kot čarovnik za preprečevanje "
"virusov uporabljata akcijo <quote>Pošlji skozi</quote> za preverjanje "
"neželene pošte/zlonamerne programske opreme. Običajno dostopni programi za "
"preprečevanje neželene pošte in protivirusni programi vrnejo sporočilo in "
"vstavijo dodaten zapis v glavi, če zaznajo neželeno pošto (ali virus)."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be cautious with this action, as it can damage your messages if the filter "
"program returns garbage or extra lines."
msgstr ""
"Pri tem dejanju bodite previdni, saj lahko poškoduje vaša sporočila, če "
"program za filtriranje vrne smeti ali dodatne vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1663
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove Header"
msgstr "Odstrani glavo"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will remove all header fields with the given name from the message. This is "
"useful mainly for removing bogus <quote>Reply-To:</quote> headers."
msgstr ""
"Iz sporočila odstrani vsa polja glave z danim imenom. To je uporabno "
"predvsem za odstranjevanje lažnih naslovov <quote>Odgovori-na:</quote>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1671
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Header"
msgstr "Dodaj glavo"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If no such field is already present this will add a new header field with "
"the given name and value to the message; if there already is a header field "
"with that name, it is overwritten with the given value; if there are already "
"multiple headers with the given name (&eg; <quote>Received:</quote> "
"headers), an arbitrary one of them is overwritten and the others are left "
"unchanged -- this is a known limitation. You may want to combine this filter "
"with the <guilabel>Remove Header</guilabel> filter above to make sure that "
"there are no other headers with that name in the message."
msgstr ""
"Če takšnega polja še ni, se v sporočilo doda novo naslovno polje z danim "
"imenom in vrednostjo; če že obstaja naslovno polje s tem imenom, se prepiše "
"z dano vrednostjo; če je že več naslovnih polj z danim imenom (npr. "
"<quote>Prejeto:</quote>), se prepiše poljubno eno od njih, druga pa ostanejo "
"nespremenjena - to je znana omejitev. Ta filter boste morda želeli "
"kombinirati z zgornjim filtrom <guilabel>Odstrani glavo</guilabel>, da se "
"prepričate, da v sporočilu ni drugih glav s tem imenom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1685
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rewrite Header"
msgstr "Prepiši glavo"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will scan the given header field, modify its contents and write it back. The "
"search string is always interpreted as a case-sensitive regular expression. "
"The replacement string is inserted literally except for occurrences of "
"<userinput>\\n</userinput>, <userinput>$n</userinput> and <userinput>${nn}</"
"userinput>, where <userinput>n</userinput> is a positive (single-digit, "
"except for the third form) number or <userinput>0</userinput>. These "
"constructs are interpreted as back references to substrings captured with "
"parentheses in the search string."
msgstr ""
"Pregleda podano polje glave, spremeni njegovo vsebino in jo zapiše nazaj. "
"Iskalni niz se vedno interpretira kot regularni izraz, ki razlikuje velike "
"in male črke. Nadomestni niz se vstavi dobesedno, razen pri pojavitvah "
"<userinput>\\n</userinput>, <userinput>$n</userinput> in <userinput>${nn}</"
"userinput>, kjer je <userinput>n</userinput> pozitivno (enomestno število, "
"razen v tretji obliki) ali <userinput>0</userinput>. Ti konstrukti se "
"razlagajo kot povratni sklici na podnize, zajete z oklepaji v iskalnem nizu."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Analogous restrictions as in the <guilabel>Add Header</guilabel> action "
"apply here, too."
msgstr ""
"Tudi tu veljajo podobne omejitve kot pri dejanju <guilabel>Dodaj glavo</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1700
#, no-c-format
msgid "Play Sound"
msgstr "Predvajaj zvok"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1702
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will play the specified sound. A browse button lets you choose a pre-"
"recorded sound (&eg; .wav) file."
msgstr ""
"Predvaja določen zvok. Z gumbom za brskanje lahko izberete vnaprej posneto "
"zvočno datoteko (&eg; .wav)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1706
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add to Address Book"
msgstr "Dodaj v imenik"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &kaddressbook; is installed, this action will let you specify which "
"header to scan (From, To, CC, or BCC), what tag to assign, if any, and which "
"named address book to store the addresses in."
msgstr ""
"Če je nameščen &kaddressbook;, lahko s tem dejanjem določite, katero glavo "
"je treba skenirati (Od, Za, CC ali BCC), katero oznako je treba dodeliti, če "
"obstaja, in v kateri imenovani imenik je treba shraniti naslove."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1714
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete Message"
msgstr "Izbriši sporočilo"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1716
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Deletes the selected message(s). Use this option cautiously. Deleted "
"messages cannot be recovered."
msgstr ""
"Izbrišite izbrano(-a) sporočilo(-a). To možnost uporabljajte previdno. "
"Izbrisanih sporočil ni mogoče obnoviti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1720
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unset Status"
msgstr "Odstrani stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1722
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the inverse of <guilabel>Mark As</guilabel>, above. Instead of "
"marking the selected message as important, read, &etc;, this action will "
"clear the specified flag."
msgstr ""
"To je obratna funkcija od zgornje funkcije <guilabel>Označi kot</guilabel>. "
"Namesto da bi izbrano sporočilo označili kot pomembno, prebrano in podobno, "
"to dejanje izbriše določeno zastavico."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1727
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encrypt"
msgstr "Šifiriraj"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1729
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will encrypt the selected message(s) with the specified public key. You may "
"choose from any public / private key pairs saved on your key ring."
msgstr ""
"Izbrana sporočila šifrira z navedenim javnim ključem. Izbirate lahko med "
"vsemi pari javnih/zasebnih ključev, shranjenimi v zbirki ključev."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:1734
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decrypt"
msgstr "Dešifriraj"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1736
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will decrypt the selected message(s). Use this action with caution. &kmail; "
"will decrypt messages automatically when you open them for viewing, so you "
"probably don't really need to use this action."
msgstr ""
"Dešifrira izbrano(-a) sporočilo(-a). To dejanje uporabljajte previdno. "
"&kmail; samodejno dešifrira sporočila, ko jih odprete za ogled, zato vam "
"tega dejanja verjetno ni treba uporabljati."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1745
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter Examples"
msgstr "Primeri filtrov"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1747
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As of yet &kmail; does not highlight or mark mails that have an extra "
"<replaceable>Priority:</replaceable> header. If you want to flag all "
"<quote>urgent</quote> messages as being <emphasis>important</emphasis>, you "
"can use a filter:"
msgstr ""
"Zaenkrat &kmail; ne izpostavi ali označi sporočil, ki imajo dodatno glavo "
"<replaceable>Prednost:</replaceable> . Če želite vsa <quote>nujna</quote> "
"sporočila označiti kot <emphasis>pomembna</emphasis>, lahko uporabite filter:"

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1753
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tagging urgent messages as <emphasis>important</emphasis>"
msgstr "Označevanje nujnih sporočil kot <emphasis>pomembnih</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open up the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"Filters...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog and click the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-new."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> New</guiicon> icon "
"below the <guilabel>Available Filters</guilabel> list."
msgstr ""
"Odprite pogovorno okno <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavljanje filtrov...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in "
"kliknite ikono <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Novo</guiicon> pod seznamom <guilabel>Na voljo so filtri</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Filter Criteria</guilabel> area, select <guilabel>Anywhere "
"in Headers</guilabel> and <guilabel>contains</guilabel> from the drop down "
"boxes and type <userinput>Priority</userinput> in the text field. Select the "
"same criterion in the next line and type <userinput>urgent</userinput> in "
"the text field of the second drop down box."
msgstr ""
"V območju <guilabel>Kriteriji filtrov</guilabel> izberite <guilabel>Kjerkoli "
"v glavi</guilabel> in <guilabel>Vključuje</guilabel> iz spustnih polj ter "
"vnesite <userinput>Prednost</userinput> v besedilno polje. V naslednji "
"vrstici izberite isto merilo in v besedilno polje drugega spustnega okna "
"vnesite <userinput>nujno</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"So your filter will match all messages containing a <quote>Priority: urgent</"
"quote> header field."
msgstr ""
"Tako bo vaš filter ustrezal vsem sporočilom, ki vsebujejo polje glave "
"<quote>Prednost: nujno</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1771
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Skip down to the <guilabel>Filter Actions</guilabel> area. Select "
"<guilabel>Mark As</guilabel> from the first drop down box. A new drop down "
"box containing a list of marker flags is shown to the right. Select "
"<guilabel>Important</guilabel> from the drop down box."
msgstr ""
"Preskočite navzdol do območja <guilabel>Dejanja filtra</guilabel>. V prvem "
"spustnem oknu izberite <guilabel>Označi kot</guilabel>. Na desni strani se "
"prikaže novo spustno okno s seznamom zastavic za označevanje. V spustnem "
"oknu izberite <guilabel>Pomembno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since you want this filter to <emphasis>not</emphasis> prevent other "
"filters' message rules from being applied, carefully <emphasis>uncheck</"
"emphasis> the <guilabel>If this filter matches, stop processing here</"
"guilabel> option on the <quote>Advanced</quote> tab."
msgstr ""
"Ker želite, da ta filter <emphasis>ne</emphasis> prepreči uporabe pravil za "
"sporočila drugih filtrov, skrbno <emphasis>odkljukajte</emphasis> možnost "
"<guilabel>Če se ta filter ujema, prenehaj z obdelavo</guilabel> na zavihku "
"<quote>Napredno</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1784
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click on <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, and you are done."
msgstr "Kliknite <guibutton>OK</guibutton> in končali ste."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1785
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Just remember to move the <quote>Priority: urgent</quote> filter entry to "
"the top of the <guilabel>Available Filters</guilabel> list each time you add "
"a new filter, so that your flow-through filter is always applied first."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite le premakniti vnosa filtra <quote>Prednost: nujno</quote> na vrh "
"seznama <guilabel>Dostopni filtri</guilabel> vsakič, ko dodate nov filter, "
"tako da se vaš pretočni filter vedno uporabi prvi."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are subscribed to the (general) &kde; List, you could create a folder "
"for the list (let's call it <replaceable>KDE-General</replaceable>) and use "
"a filter to automatically transfer new messages from your inbox to your "
"<replaceable>KDE-General</replaceable> folder if they came from the &kde; "
"List. Here is how to create this filter:"
msgstr ""
"Če ste naročeni na (splošni) seznam &kde;, lahko ustvarite mapo za seznam "
"(imenujmo jo <replaceable>KDE-Splošno</replaceable>) in uporabite filter za "
"samodejni prenos novih sporočil iz prejetih v mapo <replaceable>KDE-Splošno</"
"replaceable>, če so prišla iz seznama &kde;. Tukaj je opisano, kako "
"ustvarite ta filter:"

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1800
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filtering a mailing list"
msgstr "Filtriranje poštnega seznama"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1802
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check if <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Create filter</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Filter on Mailing-List...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"can identify the mailing list (the name of the list should then appear in "
"the menu item); in this case, this works and you are presented with a filter "
"that has <quote>List-Id <guilabel>contains</guilabel> &lt;kde.kde.org&gt;</"
"quote> preset. Then select the desired destination folder from the folder "
"pull-down menu in the <guilabel>Filter Action</guilabel> group and that is "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Preverite, ali lahko <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Izdelaj filter</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Filter na "
"poštnem seznamu...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> prepozna poštni seznam (ime "
"seznama se mora nato prikazati v meniju); v tem primeru to deluje in "
"prikazan je filter, ki ima <quote>Id-seznama<guilabel>vsebuje</guilabel> &lt;"
"kde.kde.org&gt;</quote>nastavljeno. Nato v spustnem meniju mape v skupini "
"<guilabel>Dejanja filtra</guilabel> izberite želeno ciljno mapo in to je to."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1812
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If that does not work, think of a unique way of identifying the messages you "
"want to filter. The (almost) unique property of &kde; List messages is that "
"they always contain <quote>kde@kde.org</quote> in the <guilabel>To:</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>CC:</guilabel> field. It is not quite perfect, "
"because this fails for cross-posted messages."
msgstr ""
"Če to ne deluje, si zamislite edinstven način prepoznavanja sporočil, ki jih "
"želite filtrirati. (Skoraj) edinstvena lastnost sporočil &kde; seznamov je, "
"da vedno vsebujejo <quote>kde@kde.org</quote> v polju <guilabel>Za:</"
"guilabel> ali <guilabel>CC:</guilabel>. Delovanje ni povsem popolno, saj to "
"ne uspe pri navzkrižno poslanih sporočilih."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"Filters...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>, Nastavi "
"filtre...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guibutton> button to create an empty filter. It will appear as <guilabel>&lt;"
"unknown&gt;</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"document-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject></guibutton>, da ustvarite prazen filter. Pojavi se kot "
"<guilabel>&lt;unknown&gt;</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel> Filter Criteria</guilabel> area, select <guilabel>All "
"Recipients</guilabel> from the first drop down box, <guilabel>contains</"
"guilabel> from the second drop down box, and type <userinput>kde@kde.org</"
"userinput> in the text field."
msgstr ""
"V območju <guilabel>Kriteriji filtra</guilabel> izberite <guilabel>Vsi "
"prejemniki</guilabel> iz prvega spustnega polja, <guilabel>vsebuje</"
"guilabel> iz drugega spustnega polja in vnesite <userinput>kde@kde.org</"
"userinput> v besedilno polje."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Skip down to the <guilabel>Filter Actions</guilabel> section. Select "
"<guilabel>Move Into Folder</guilabel> from the first drop down box. Click on "
"the folder icon and a window containing a list of folders will appear. "
"Select the folder that you want the filtered messages to be transferred to. "
"For this example, you would select <guilabel>KDE-General</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Preskočite do razdelka <guilabel>Dejanja filtra</guilabel>. V prvem spustnem "
"oknu izberite <guilabel>Premakni v mapo</guilabel>. Kliknite ikono mape in "
"prikazalo se bo okno s seznamom map. Izberite mapo, v katero želite prenesti "
"filtrirana sporočila. V tem primeru izberete <guilabel>KDE-Splošno</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1844
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may find that you need to use more powerful criteria to properly filter "
"your messages; for example, you may only want to filter the &kde; List "
"messages that are written by your friend <replaceable>Fred Johnson &lt;"
"fj@anywhere.com&gt;</replaceable>. This is where the rest of the matching "
"criteria section comes into play:"
msgstr ""
"Morda boste za pravilno filtriranje sporočil morali uporabiti močnejša "
"merila; morda boste na primer želeli filtrirati samo sporočila iz seznama "
"sporočil &kde;, ki jih je napisal vaš prijatelj <replaceable>Franc Novak &lt;"
"fn@kjerkoli.com&gt;</replaceable>. V tem razdelku so na voljo preostala "
"merila za ujemanje:"

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1851
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extending the filter"
msgstr "Razširitev filtra"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1853
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open up the <guilabel>Configure Filters...</guilabel> window and select the "
"filter you just created."
msgstr ""
"Odprite okno <guilabel>Nastavi Filtre...</guilabel> in izberite filter, ki "
"ste ga pravkar ustvarili."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1857
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since you want to filter all messages that have <replaceable>kde@kde.org</"
"replaceable> in the <guilabel>To:</guilabel> or <guilabel>CC:</guilabel> "
"field <emphasis>and</emphasis> that are from Fred, check the "
"<guibutton>Match all of the following</guibutton> radio button."
msgstr ""
"Ker želite filtrirati vsa sporočila, ki imajo v polju <guilabel>Za:</"
"guilabel> ali <guilabel>CC:</guilabel> <emphasis>in</emphasis>, ki so od "
"Franca, označite izbirni gumb <guibutton>Naj se ujema vse od naslednjega</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1865
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now, go to the second search rule and select the following from the pull-"
"down menus: <guilabel>From</guilabel>, <guilabel>contains</guilabel>. Now, "
"type <userinput>fj@anywhere.com</userinput> in the text field."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj pojdite na drugo pravilo iskanja in v spustnih menijih izberite "
"naslednje: <guilabel>Od</guilabel>, <guilabel>obsega</guilabel>. V besedilno "
"polje vnesite <userinput>fn@kjerkoli.com</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You now have a filter that identifies all &kde; List messages that are from "
"<userinput>fj@anywhere.com</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj imate filter, ki identificira vsa sporočila seznama &kde;, ki so od "
"<userinput>fn@kjerkoli.com</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1880
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter Optimization"
msgstr "Optimizacija filtra"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1882
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is important to realize that the order of the filters has an impact on "
"the speed of the filtering process. Here are some ideas which can help you "
"to improve filter performance."
msgstr ""
"Pomembno je vedeti, da vrstni red filtrov vpliva na hitrost postopka "
"filtriranja. Tukaj je nekaj idej, ki vam lahko pomagajo izboljšati delovanje "
"filtra."

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:1889
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stop filter processing as soon as possible:"
msgstr "Čim prej zaustavite obdelavo filtra:"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you know that a filter finally processes a certain class of messages, "
"please make sure to check the option <guilabel>If this filter matches, stop "
"processing here</guilabel> for the filter. This will avoid the evaluation of "
"the filter rules of all subsequent filters. (See the advanced options in the "
"<link linkend=\"filter-dialog-id\"> Filter Dialog</link>)."
msgstr ""
"Če veste, da filter dokončno obdela določen razred sporočil, preverite "
"možnost <guilabel>Če se filter ujema, prekini obdelavo</guilabel> za filter. "
"S tem se izognete ocenjevanju pravil filtriranja vseh naslednjih filtrov. "
"(Oglejte si napredne možnosti v <link linkend=\"filter-dialog-id\"> "
"Pogovornem oknu za filtriranje</link>)."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1897
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An example is filtering messages from mailing lists via List-Id header into "
"separate folders. Having found out that a message came from list A means "
"that you can avoid checking the next filter for messages from list B."
msgstr ""
"Primer je filtriranje sporočil iz poštnih seznamov prek glave Id-jev-eznama "
"v ločene mape. Če ste ugotovili, da je sporočilo prišlo s seznama A, se "
"lahko izognete preverjanju naslednjega filtra za sporočila s seznama B."

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:1906
#, no-c-format
msgid "Consider the costs of the evaluation of filter rules:"
msgstr "Upoštevajte stroške vrednotenja pravil filtriranja:"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The time required to evaluate a filter rule depends on the way the rule is "
"constructed. In particular, scanning for a substring using the "
"<guilabel>contains</guilabel> operation is faster than a pattern matching "
"using the <guilabel>matches regular expr.</guilabel> operation."
msgstr ""
"Čas, potreben za ovrednotenje pravila filtra, je odvisen od načina izdelave "
"pravila. Zlasti iskanje podniza z uporabo operacije <guilabel>vsebuje</"
"guilabel> je hitrejše od iskanja vzorca z uporabo operacije "
"<guilabel>ustreza regularnemu izrazu</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1914
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another dependency is on the amount of data which is used for the evaluation "
"of a filter rule. If the rule is based on a message header, its evaluation "
"should normally be much faster than the evaluation of a rule based on the "
"complete message."
msgstr ""
"Druga odvisnost je odvisna od količine podatkov, ki se uporabljajo za "
"vrednotenje pravila filtra. Če pravilo temelji na glavi sporočila, mora biti "
"njegovo vrednotenje običajno veliko hitrejše od vrednotenja pravila, ki "
"temelji na celotnem sporočilu."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1919
#, no-c-format
msgid "Try to keep the filter rules as simple as possible."
msgstr "Pravila filtriranja naj bodo čim bolj preprosta."

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:1926
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check the order of your filters:"
msgstr "Preverite vrstni red filtrov:"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1928
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The various filter actions have different degrees of complexity. The most "
"expensive filter actions are <guilabel>Pipe Through</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Execute Command</guilabel>, because both need external programs to "
"be run. Placing filters containing these filter actions behind other filters "
"that can reduce the number of times these complex actions are required is "
"useful, if the filter logic allows this."
msgstr ""
"Različni postopki filtriranja so različno zapleteni. Najdražji akciji "
"filtriranja sta <guilabel>Pošlji skozi</guilabel> in <guilabel>Izvedi ukaz</"
"guilabel>, saj je pri obeh treba zagnati zunanje programe. Če logika filtra "
"to omogoča, je koristno filtre, ki vsebujejo ta dejanja filtriranja, "
"postaviti za druge filtre, ki lahko zmanjšajo število primerov, ko so ta "
"zapletena dejanja potrebna."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1935
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An example is filtering messages from a mailing list and detecting spam "
"messages. For the spam detection you will usually use an external tool via a "
"<guilabel>Pipe Through</guilabel> action. Filtering the messages for the "
"mailing list is done via the List-Id header. If you do not want to check the "
"messages from the mailing list for spam too, it is better to use the filter "
"for the mailing list messages before the filter for the spam detection. This "
"way you avoid the expensive and slow spam check for all messages which were "
"identified as mailing list messages."
msgstr ""
"Primer je filtriranje sporočil s poštnega seznama in odkrivanje neželenih "
"sporočil. Za zaznavanje neželene pošte se običajno uporablja zunanje orodje "
"z dejanjem <guilabel>Pretoči skozi</guilabel>. Filtriranje sporočil za "
"poštni seznam se izvede z glavo Id-ja-Seznama. Če ne želite preverjati tudi "
"sporočil iz poštnega seznama za neželeno pošto, je bolje, da uporabite "
"filter za sporočila poštnega seznama pred filtrom za odkrivanje neželene "
"pošte. Tako se izognete dragemu in počasnemu preverjanju neželene pošte za "
"vsa sporočila, ki so bila prepoznana kot sporočila s poštnega seznama."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1950
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter Log"
msgstr "Denvnik filtrov"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to verify that your filters work as intended, you can open a "
"viewer for the filter log via <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Filter Log Viewer...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preveriti, ali filtri delujejo, kot je bilo predvideno, lahko prek "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pregledovalnik dnevnika "
"filtra...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> odprete pregledovalnik dnevnika filtra."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1955
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the viewer you can configure logging of the filter process. You can "
"control the level of detail recorded, clear the log, limit the size of the "
"log, and save the log as a file. The log can provide valuable information "
"when you want to improve your filter rules."
msgstr ""
"V pregledovalniku lahko konfigurirate beleženje postopka filtriranja. "
"Določite lahko raven zabeleženih podrobnosti, izbrišete dnevnik, omejite "
"velikost dnevnika in ga shranite v datoteko. Dnevnik lahko zagotovi "
"dragocene informacije, ko želite izboljšati pravila filtriranja."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1964
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backing up &kmail;"
msgstr "Varnostno kopiranje za &kmail;"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1965
#, no-c-format
msgid "This section describes various backup solutions within &kmail;."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku so opisane različne rešitve za varnostno kopiranje v sistemu "
"&kmail;."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:1967
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archiving"
msgstr "Arhiviranje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kmail.docbook:1970
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Archive Folder...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Arhiviraj mapo...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1972
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature is also available through the context menu launched with a "
"&RMB;, then select <guimenuitem>Archive Folder...</guimenuitem>. This will "
"<action>open a dialog</action> that allows you to create a single archive of "
"the currently selected folder."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija je na voljo tudi prek kontekstnega menija, ki ga zaženete z "
"&RMB;, nato izberite <guimenuitem>Arhiviraj mapo...</guimenuitem>. To bo "
"<action>odprlo pogovorno okno</action>, ki omogoča ustvarjanje enega samega "
"arhiva trenutno izbrane mape."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1974
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Folder:</guilabel> shows the currently selected folder, if you "
"wish to change the folder to be archived click the folder icon. The "
"<guilabel>Format:</guilabel> drop down menu allows you to choose a format "
"(choices are: zip, tar, tar.bz2, and tar.gz). If you would like to change "
"the default name or location, click the folder button to the right of "
"<guilabel>Archive File</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Mapa:</guilabel> prikazuje trenutno izbrano mapo, če želite "
"spremeniti mapo za arhiviranje, kliknite ikono mape. V spustnem meniju "
"<guilabel>Format:</guilabel> lahko izberete format (možnosti so: zip, tar, "
"tar.bz2 in tar.gz). Če želite spremeniti privzeto ime ali lokacijo, kliknite "
"gumb za mapo na desni strani <guilabel>Arhivska datoteka</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1977
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the <guilabel>Delete folder and subfolders after completion</guilabel> "
"button if you would like everything you archived deleted from the &kmail; "
"database after the external archive has been saved. By default all "
"subfolders will be archived. Uncheck <guilabel>Archive all subfolders</"
"guilabel> if you only want to archive the parent folder."
msgstr ""
"Označite gumb <guilabel>Po zaključku izbriši mapo in podmape</guilabel>, če "
"želite, da se po shranjevanju zunanjega arhiva iz podatkovne baze &kmail; "
"izbriše vse, kar ste arhivirali. Privzeto bodo arhivirane vse podmape. Če "
"želite arhivirati samo nadrejeno mapo, odstranite potrditev "
"<guilabel>Arhiviraj vse podmape</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kmail.docbook:1982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Automatic Archiving...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavi samodejno arhiviranje...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:1984
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a powerful tool that can be used to assist in backing up your email. "
"Please see <ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_archivemail_agent\">Automatic "
"Archiving</ulink> for details."
msgstr ""
"To je zmogljivo orodje, s katerim si lahko pomagate pri varnostnem kopiranju "
"e-pošte. Za podrobnosti glejte <ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_archivemail_agent"
"\">Samodejno arhiviranje</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2038
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exporting"
msgstr "Izvažanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kmail.docbook:2041
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Import/Export &kmail; Data...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi/Izvozi podatke &kmail;-a...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2043
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature exports settings and local mail to a compressed file. Please "
"see <ulink url=\"help:/pimdataexporter\">pim data exporter</ulink> for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija izvozi nastavitve in lokalno pošto v stisnjeno datoteko. Za "
"podrobnosti glejte <ulink url=\"help:/pimdataexporter\">izvoznik podatkov "
"pim</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2050
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restore and Import in &kmail;"
msgstr "Obnovitev in uvoz v &kmail;"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section describes restoring backups and importing data into &kmail;."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku sta opisana obnavljanje varnostnih kopij in uvoz podatkov v "
"&kmail;."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2054
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restoring backed up email and settings"
msgstr "Obnovitev varnostne kopije e-pošte in nastavitev"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kmail.docbook:2057
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Export &kmail; Data...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvozi podatke &kmail;-a...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2059
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you used PIM Data Exporter to backup local email and / or settings, "
"please use it again to restore data into &kmail;. See <ulink url=\"help:/"
"pimdataexporter\">PIM Data Exporter</ulink> for details."
msgstr ""
"Če ste za varnostno kopiranje lokalne e-pošte in/ali nastavitev uporabili "
"izvoznik podatkov PIM, ga ponovno uporabite za obnovitev podatkov v &kmail;. "
"Za podrobnosti glejte <ulink url=\"help:/pimdataexporter\">Izvoznik podatkov "
"PIM</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2066
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing options in &kmail;"
msgstr "Uvoz možnosti v &kmail;"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2068
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; has an import wizard to make the transition from another email "
"application easier."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; ima čarovnika za uvoz, ki olajša prehod iz druge e-poštne aplikacije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kmail.docbook:2074
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import from another Email Client...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uvoz iz drugega e-poštnega "
"odjemalca...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2079
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This starts the import wizard and tries to automatically detect data from "
"another email application. In case the mail data you want to import is not "
"found, use the <guilabel>Manual Selection</guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"S tem se začne čarovnik za uvoz in poskuša samodejno zaznati podatke iz "
"druge e-poštne aplikacije. Če podatkov o pošti, ki jih želite uvoziti, ne "
"najdete, uporabite možnost <guilabel>Ročna izbira</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: using-kmail.docbook:2085
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-import.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Import Messages...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-import.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Uvozi sporočila...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2089
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts the import wizard and lets you select the desired data manually."
msgstr "Začne se čarovnik za uvoz in omogoči ročno izbiro želenih podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2093
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please read the <ulink url=\"help:/importwizard\">Import Wizard</ulink> "
"documentation for details."
msgstr ""
"Za podrobnosti preberite dokumentacijo <ulink url=\"help:/importwizard"
"\">Čarovnik za uvoz</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Multiple Accounts"
msgstr "Uporaba večih računov"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Multiple accounts are used to check for messages from more than one email "
"address and/or mail server. Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"configurebutton.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Configure &kmail;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and click on the "
"<guilabel>Accounts</guilabel> page to add or change your account settings. "
"See the <link linkend=\"getting-started\">Getting started</link> section for "
"more information on the settings in the <guilabel>Accounts</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"Več računov se uporablja za preverjanje sporočil z več kot enega e-poštnega "
"naslova in/ali poštnega strežnika. Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"configurebutton.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Nastavi &kmail;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in kliknite stran "
"<guilabel>Računi</guilabel>, da dodate ali spremenite nastavitve računa. Za "
"več informacij o nastavitvah na strani <guilabel>Računi</guilabel> glejte "
"razdelek <link linkend=\"getting-started\">Kako začeti</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To check for messages from a particular account, use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-receive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Check Mail In</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"submenu to select the account to check for mail. You can also press and hold "
"the &LMB; on the <guiicon><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"mail-receive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> Check Mail</guiicon> icon (on the toolbar) for a few "
"seconds to get a list of accounts."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preveriti sporočila iz določenega računa, uporabite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-receive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Preglej pošto v</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"podmeni, da izberete račun za preverjanje pošte. Lahko tudi pritisnete in za "
"nekaj sekund pridržite &LMB; na ikoni <guiicon><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-receive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Preveri pošto</guiicon> (v orodni vrstici), "
"da dobite seznam računov."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Signing and Encrypting Messages with <application>GnuPG</application>"
msgstr "Podpisovanje in šifriranje sporočil z <application>GnuPG</application>"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a short introduction on how to set up &kmail;'s <application>GnuPG</"
"application> (<application>&GNU; Privacy Guard</application>) support; it "
"gives some hints on the use of <application>GnuPG</application> too. It is "
"written for people who are beginners in this area; if you are familiar with "
"the use of <application>GnuPG</application>, you can skip most of the steps."
msgstr ""
"To je kratek uvod o tem, kako nastaviti podporo <application>GnuPG</"
"application> (<application>&GNU; stražar zasebnosti</application>) v &kmail; "
"vsebuje tudi nekaj namigov o uporabi <application>GnuPG</application>. "
"Napisan je za začetnike na tem področju; če poznate uporabo "
"<application>GnuPG</application>, lahko večino korakov preskočite."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please also check out the <link linkend=\"pgp-faq\">&FAQ; item about "
"<application>GnuPG</application></link>."
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si tudi <link linkend=\"pgp-faq\">odsek &FAQ; o <application>GnuPG</"
"application></link>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Attachments will not be signed/encrypted if you are using inline OpenPGP. To "
"sign/encrypt attachments, you have to install GnuPG and some necessary "
"libraries. Then, you can decide for each attachment whether it should be "
"signed/encrypted or not."
msgstr ""
"Priponke ne bodo podpisane/šifrirane, če uporabljate vgrajeni OpenPGP. Za "
"podpisovanje/šifriranje priponk morate namestiti program GnuPG in nekatere "
"potrebne knjižnice. Nato se lahko za vsako priponko odločite, ali naj bo "
"podpisana/šifrirana ali ne."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set up and use <application>GnuPG</application> support in &kmail; it is "
"necessary to have <application>GnuPG</application> installed and configured "
"properly. Of course, we cannot give you a full introduction to "
"<application>GnuPG</application> here. We will only mention the steps you "
"must perform to get <application>GnuPG</application> going. For details you "
"should look at <ulink url=\"https://www.gnupg.org/docs.html#guides\">The "
"&GNU; Privacy Handbook</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za nastavitev in uporabo podpore <application>GnuPG</application> v &kmail;-"
"u je treba imeti nameščeno in pravilno konfigurirano <application>GnuPG</"
"application>. Seveda vam tukaj ne moremo v celoti predstaviti "
"<application>GnuPG</application>. Omenili bomo le korake, ki jih morate "
"opraviti, da boste lahko začeli uporabljati <application>GnuPG</"
"application>. Podrobnosti najdete v <ulink url=\"https://www.gnupg.org/docs."
"html#guides\">Priročniku o zasebnosti</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is certainly a good idea to study the GnuPG documentation as well as an "
"introduction to public key cryptography. That way you can learn a lot about "
"the basic concepts, which will help you understand what is going on. Also, "
"many security related issues you should know about are discussed there."
msgstr ""
"Vsekakor je dobro preučiti dokumentacijo GnuPG in uvod v kriptografijo "
"javnih ključev. Tako se boste lahko naučili veliko o osnovnih konceptih, kar "
"vam bo pomagalo razumeti, kaj se dogaja. Obravnavana so tudi številne "
"težave, povezane z varnostjo, o katerih morate vedeti."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preconditions"
msgstr "Predpogoji"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; expects that your <application>GnuPG</application> binary is called "
"<command>gpg</command>. If this is not the case for you, just make a symlink."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; pričakuje, da se vaša <application>GnuPG</application> imenuje "
"<command>gpg</command>. Če vam to ne ustreza, ustvarite simbolno povezavo."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have not yet done so, you must generate a key pair (secret and public "
"keys) for your identity. You may do this using &kgpg; or &kleopatra; or at "
"the command line: <userinput><command>gpg</command> <option>--gen-key</"
"option></userinput>. Or you can ask &kmail; to create a new key pair when "
"you create a new email account. The identity (normally your name followed by "
"your email address within brackets, such as <userinput>John Doe &lt;"
"john@example.com&gt;</userinput>) and your passphrase are important for the "
"co-operation between &kmail; and <application>GnuPG</application>."
msgstr ""
"Če tega še niste storili, morate za svojo identiteto ustvariti par ključev "
"(tajni in javni ključ). To lahko storite z uporabo &kgpg; ali &kleopatra; "
"ali v ukazni vrstici: <userinput><command>gpg</command> <option>--gen-key</"
"option></userinput>. Lahko pa tudi prosite &kmail;, da ob ustvarjanju novega "
"e-poštnega računa ustvari nov par ključev. Identiteta (običajno vašemu imenu "
"sledi vaš e-poštni naslov v oklepaju, na primer <userinput>Marija Novak &lt;"
"marija@primer.com&gt;</userinput>) in geslo sta pomembna za sodelovanje med "
"&kmail; in <application>GnuPG</application>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2191
#, no-c-format
msgid "<application>GnuPG</application>-Related Settings in &kmail;"
msgstr "<application>GnuPG</application>-Sorodne nastavitve v &kmail;-u"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>Composing</guilabel> tab on the <guilabel>Security</"
"guilabel> settings page. There you will find the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Na strani z nastavitvami <guilabel>Sestavljanje</guilabel> izberite zavihek "
"<guilabel>Varnost</guilabel>. Tam boste našli naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:2212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When encrypting emails, always also encrypt to the certificate of my own "
"identity"
msgstr ""
"Pri šifriranju e-poštnih sporočil vedno šifrirajte tudi s potrdilom lastne "
"identitete"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is off and you want to send an encrypted message to somebody, "
"then you cannot read this message any longer after you have composed and "
"encrypted it. Turn this option on to keep the encrypted messages you send "
"readable for you, too."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost izklopljena in želite nekomu poslati šifrirano sporočilo, "
"tega sporočila po sestavi in šifriranju ne morete več prebrati. Če to "
"možnost vklopite, bodo šifrirana sporočila, ki jih pošiljate, berljiva tudi "
"za vas."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:2222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Store sent messages encrypted"
msgstr "Shranjevanje poslanih sporočil v šifrirani obliki"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this box is checked, sent messages are stored encrypted, as they were "
"sent. This is not recommended, as you will not be able to read the messages "
"any longer if a necessary certificate expires. (Notice that GPG keys do not "
"expire, as a general rule; this caution is primarily relevant for x.509 "
"certificate users.)"
msgstr ""
"Ko je to polje označeno, so poslana sporočila shranjena šifrirano, kot so "
"bila poslana. To ni priporočljivo, saj sporočil ne boste mogli več brati, če "
"poteče veljavnost potrebnega potrdila. (Upoštevajte, da veljavnost ključev "
"GPG praviloma ne poteče; to opozorilo velja predvsem za uporabnike potrdil "
"x.509.)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:2232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Always show the encryption keys for approval"
msgstr "Vedno pokažite šifrirne ključe za odobritev"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will always open a dialog that lets you choose the keys used for each "
"recipient when you are sending an encrypted message. If this option is off, "
"&kmail; will show the dialog only when it cannot find a key for a recipient "
"or when there are conflicting or unset encryption preferences."
msgstr ""
"To vedno odpre pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko pri pošiljanju šifriranega "
"sporočila izberete ključe, ki se uporabljajo za vsakega prejemnika. Če je ta "
"možnost izklopljena, bo &kmail; prikazal pogovorno okno le, če ne more najti "
"ključa za prejemnika ali če so si nastavitve šifriranja nasprotujoče ali "
"niso nastavljene."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:2243
#, no-c-format
msgid "When saving as draft, always sign/encrypt as indicated"
msgstr ""
"Pri shranjevanju kot osnutek vedno podpišite/šifrirajte, kot je navedeno"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is on, &kmail; will automatically encrypt (and / or sign) "
"messages that you save in the <guilabel>drafts</guilabel> folder (when you "
"specify signing / encryption)."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost vklopljena, bo &kmail; samodejno šifriral (in/ali podpisal) "
"sporočila, ki jih shranite v mapo <guilabel>osnutki</guilabel> (ko določite "
"podpisovanje/šifriranje)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: using-kmail.docbook:2249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show sign/encrypt indicator in editor"
msgstr "Prikaži indikator podpisa/šifriranja v urejevalniku"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is on, &kmail; will display an indicator in the composition "
"window to inform you that this message will be signed / encrypted whenever "
"that is the case."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost vklopljena, bo &kmail; v oknu sestave prikazal indikator, "
"ki vas bo obvestil, da bo to sporočilo podpisano/šifrirano, kadarkoli bo to "
"potrebno."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that you have set up the encryption tool, you must tell &kmail; which "
"OpenPGP key you want to use for signing and encrypting messages. To do this "
"go to the <link linkend=\"configure-identity\">Identities configuration</"
"link> and set the key that should be used via the <guilabel>Cryptography</"
"guilabel> tab in the identity configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste nastavili orodje za šifriranje, morate sporočiti, kateri ključ "
"OpenPGP želite uporabiti za podpisovanje in šifriranje sporočil. To storite "
"v <link linkend=\"configure-identity\">Nastavitve identitet</link> in "
"nastavite ključ, ki naj se uporabi, prek zavihka <guilabel>Kriptografija</"
"guilabel> v pogovornem oknu za nastavitev identitete."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you can sign outgoing messages. To let people send you encrypted "
"messages, and to let them verify your signature, you must send them your "
"public key, or upload your public key to a public <application>GnuPG</"
"application> key server (so people can fetch your key from the server). To "
"send encrypted messages to other people, or to verify their signed messages, "
"you will need their public keys. You can search for public keys on a public "
"<application>GnuPG</application> key server. Or you can ask your friends to "
"send you one or more of their public keys."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj lahko podpišete odhodna sporočila. Če želite, da vam ljudje pošiljajo "
"šifrirana sporočila in preverjajo vaš podpis, jim morate poslati svoj javni "
"ključ ali naložiti svoj javni ključ v javni <application>GnuPG</application> "
"strežnik ključev (tako da lahko ljudje vaš ključ pridobijo iz strežnika). Za "
"pošiljanje šifriranih sporočil drugim osebam ali preverjanje njihovih "
"podpisanih sporočil potrebujete njihove javne ključe. Javne ključe lahko "
"poiščete v javnem strežniku ključev <application>GnuPG</application>. Lahko "
"pa prosite prijatelje, da vam pošljejo enega ali več svojih javnih ključev."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2274
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sign your Messages"
msgstr "Podpišite svoja sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compose your message as usual in the composer window. Before you send the "
"message, check the <guibutton><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"document-edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> Sign</guibutton> icon on the toolbar of the composer "
"window, or select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Options</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"document-edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"Sign Message</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Then, you can send the message. The "
"identity you are using to write the current message needs to be connected to "
"an <guilabel>OpenPGP Key</guilabel> in the <guilabel>Identity</guilabel> "
"section of the <guilabel>Configure</guilabel> dialog. To sign the message, "
"&kmail; needs to know your <application>GnuPG</application> passphrase. You "
"may be asked to supply it, or, if you have previously given the phrase to "
"&kmail;, the message will be signed automatically."
msgstr ""
"Sporočilo sestavite kot običajno v oknu skladatelja. Preden pošljete "
"sporočilo, preverite ikono <guibutton><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Podpiši</guibutton> v orodni vrstici okna "
"sestavljavca ali izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Možnosti</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"document-edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"Podpiši sporočilo</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Nato lahko pošljete sporočilo. "
"Identiteta, ki jo uporabljate za pisanje trenutnega sporočila, mora biti "
"povezana s ključem <guilabel>OpenPGP Key</guilabel> v razdelku "
"<guilabel>Identiteta</guilabel> pogovornega okna <guilabel>Configure</"
"guilabel>. Za podpis sporočila mora &kmail; poznati vašo <application>GnuPG</"
"application> geslo. Morda boste pozvani, da ga navedete, če pa ste že prej "
"navedli geslo v &kmail;-u, bo sporočilo podpisano samodejno."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encrypt your Messages"
msgstr "Šifrirajte svoja sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To send an encrypted message to somebody whose public key is on your gpg key "
"ring, simply create the message in the composer window. Before you send the "
"message, check the <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"document-decrypt.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> Encrypt</guibutton> button in the toolbar of the composer "
"window (or select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Options</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"document-decrypt.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Encrypt Message</guimenuitem></menuchoice>). Then send the message."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nekomu, čigar javni ključ je v zbirki ključev gpg, poslati "
"šifrirano sporočilo, ga preprosto ustvarite v oknu Composer. Preden pošljete "
"sporočilo, preverite gumb <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"document-decrypt.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> Šifriraj</guibutton> v orodni vrstici okna skladatelja "
"(ali izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Možnosti</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"document-decrypt.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"Šifriraj sporočilo</guimenuitem></menuchoice>). Nato pošljite sporočilo."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you checked the <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"document-decrypt.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> Encrypt</guibutton> button and &kmail; cannot find a "
"matching key for a recipient, it will allow you to modify your key ring "
"before trying again. If &kmail; finds more than one trusted key for a "
"recipient, it will display a list containing all matching keys for this "
"recipient. In either case you can select the key(s) which should be used for "
"encrypting this message for the recipient in question."
msgstr ""
"Če ste označili gumb <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"document-decrypt.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> Šifriranje</guibutton> in &kmail; ne more najti "
"ustreznega ključa za prejemnika, vam bo pred ponovnim poskusom omogočil "
"spremembo zbirke ključev. Če &kmail; za prejemnika najde več kot en zaupanja "
"vreden ključ, prikaže seznam z vsemi ustreznimi ključi za tega prejemnika. V "
"obeh primerih lahko izberete ključ(e), ki naj se uporabijo za šifriranje "
"tega sporočila za tega prejemnika."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are using a key for the first time, if there are conflicting "
"Encryption Preferences, or if <guilabel>Always show the encryption keys for "
"approval</guilabel> is selected in the <guilabel>Security</guilabel> section "
"of &kmail;'s configuration dialog, the <guilabel>Encryption Key Approval</"
"guilabel> dialog will appear. You can select different keys for the "
"recipients and can set the <guilabel>Encryption Preference</guilabel> for "
"each recipient. The option, <guilabel>Encrypt whenever encryption is "
"possible</guilabel> (on the <guilabel>Cryptography</guilabel> tab of the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kmail;...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> dialog), will automatically encrypt your message "
"if there is a trusted key for each recipient."
msgstr ""
"Če ključ uporabljate prvič: če obstajajo nasprotujoče si nastavitve "
"šifriranja ali če je v razdelku <guilabel>Vedno prikaži šifrirne ključe v "
"odobritev</guilabel> v razdelku <guilabel>Varnost</guilabel> v pogovornem "
"oknu za nastavljanje storitve &kmail; izbrana možnost <guilabel>Potrditev "
"šifrirnih ključev</guilabel>, se prikaže pogovorno okno <guilabel>Potrditev "
"šifrirnih ključev</guilabel>. Za prejemnike lahko izberete različne ključe "
"in za vsakega prejemnika nastavite <guilabel>Prednost šifriranja</guilabel>. "
"Z možnostjo <guilabel>Šifriraj, kadar je šifriranje mogoče</guilabel> (na "
"zavihku <guilabel>Kriptografija</guilabel> pogovornega okna "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavi &kmail;...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>) bo sporočilo samodejno šifrirano, če je za "
"vsakega prejemnika na voljo zanesljiv ključ."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As mentioned above, you will not be able to read your own encrypted sent "
"messages if you do not check <guilabel>When encrypting emails, always also "
"encrypt to the certificate of my own identity</guilabel> in the settings' "
"<guilabel>Security</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"Kot je navedeno zgoraj, ne boste mogli prebrati lastnih šifriranih poslanih "
"sporočil, če na strani <guilabel>Za šifriranje e-poštnih sporočil vedno "
"šifrirajte tudi s potrdilom moje identitete</guilabel> na strani "
"<guilabel>Varnost</guilabel> v nastavitvah."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Send your Public Key"
msgstr "Pošljite vaš javni ključ"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Prepare a message to the person to whom you want to send your public key. "
"Then choose, in the composer window's menu, <menuchoice><guimenu>Attach</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Attach Public Key</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This will "
"attach your public key – the one you are currently using – to the message."
msgstr ""
"Pripravite sporočilo osebi, ki ji želite poslati svoj javni ključ. Nato v "
"meniju okna sestavljalnika izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Pripni</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pripni javni ključ</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
"Sporočilu bo priložen vaš javni ključ - tisti, ki ga trenutno uporabljate."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remember that it is not perfectly safe to just sign the message to ensure "
"that the receiver gets the correct key. There can (possibly) be a \"man-in-"
"the-middle\" attack: somebody could intercept your message, change the "
"attached key, and then sign the message with that other key. The recipient "
"should verify the attached key by checking the key's fingerprint against the "
"one he received in a secure way from you. Alternatively, just ask him to use "
"the key he received to compose and send an encrypted message back to you. If "
"your secret key decrypts that message, he has a copy of your public key. See "
"the <application>GnuPG</application> documentation for further details."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite, da ni povsem varno, če sporočilo samo podpišete, da bi "
"zagotovili, da prejemnik dobi pravilen ključ. Lahko (morda) pride do napada "
"\"osebe na sredini angl. man-in-the-middle attack\": ko nekdo prestreže vaše "
"sporočilo, spremeni priloženi ključ in nato podpiše sporočilo s tem drugim "
"ključem. Prejemnik mora priloženi ključ preveriti tako, da preveri prstni "
"odtis ključa s tistim, ki ga je na varen način prejel od vas. Lahko ga tudi "
"prosite, naj s prejetim ključem sestavi in vam pošlje šifrirano sporočilo. "
"Če vaš tajni ključ dešifrira to sporočilo, ima kopijo vašega javnega ključa. "
"Za več podrobnosti glejte dokumentacijo <application>GnuPG</application>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2360
#, no-c-format
msgid "You received an encrypted Message"
msgstr "Prejeli ste šifrirano sporočilo"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All you have to do is to select the message in &kmail;. You may be prompted "
"for your passphrase. Then, &kmail; will decrypt the message and show you the "
"plain text if the message was encrypted with your public key. If not, you "
"will not be able to read it. By default, &kmail; stores messages encrypted, "
"so nobody can read these messages without knowing your passphrase, or, at a "
"minimum, your login password."
msgstr ""
"Vse, kar morate storiti, je, da izberete sporočilo v &kmail;-u. Morda boste "
"pozvani k vnosu gesla. Nato bo &kmail; dešifriral sporočilo in prikazal "
"navadno besedilo, če je bilo sporočilo šifrirano z vašim javnim ključem. V "
"nasprotnem primeru ga ne boste mogli prebrati. Privzeto &kmail; sporočila "
"shranjuje šifrirano, zato jih nihče ne more prebrati, če ne pozna vašega "
"gesla ali vsaj prijavnega gesla."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2371
#, no-c-format
msgid "Receiving a Public Key"
msgstr "Prejem javnega ključa"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can receive a public key as an attachment, or via http, ftp, or a "
"floppy. Before you use this key to encrypt a message to the owner of the "
"key, you should verify the key (check its fingerprint or look for trusted "
"signatures); then, you can add this key to your public keyring by typing "
"<userinput><command>gpg</command> <option>--import</option> "
"<replaceable>filename</replaceable></userinput> at the command line. If the "
"key is not certified with another signature that you have already trusted, "
"you cannot use it to encrypt messages unless you sign (certify) the key with "
"your own key."
msgstr ""
"Javni ključ lahko prejmete kot priponko ali prek protokola http, ftp ali "
"diskete. Preden ta ključ uporabite za šifriranje sporočila lastniku ključa, "
"morate ključ preveriti (preverite njegov prstni odtis ali poiščite zaupanja "
"vredne podpise); nato lahko ta ključ dodate v svoj javni sveženj ključev "
"tako, da v ukazno vrstico vnesete <userinput><command>gpg</command> "
"<option>--import</option> <replaceable>imedatoteke</replaceable></"
"userinput>. Če ključ ni potrjen z drugim podpisom, ki ste mu že zaupali, ga "
"ne morete uporabiti za šifriranje sporočil, razen če ključ podpišete "
"(potrdite) z lastnim ključem."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2388
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Anti-Spam Wizard"
msgstr "Čarovnik proti neželeni pošti"

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2391 using-kmail.docbook:2572
#, no-c-format
msgid "Basics"
msgstr "Osnove"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; does not have a built-in spam detection solution: the developers "
"believe using external, but specialized, tools is the better approach. "
"&kmail; uses these tools through its flexible filter architecture. The Anti-"
"Spam Wizard helps you with the initial filter setup."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; nima vgrajene rešitve za odkrivanje neželene pošte: razvijalci "
"menijo, da je uporaba zunanjih, vendar specializiranih orodij boljši "
"pristop. &kmail; uporablja ta orodja prek svoje prilagodljive arhitekture "
"filtrov. Čarovnik za preprečevanje neželene pošte vam pomaga pri začetni "
"nastavitvi filtra."

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:2401 using-kmail.docbook:2582
#, no-c-format
msgid "What can the wizard do to help you?"
msgstr "Kaj lahko čarovnik stori, da vam pomaga?"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It will give you some choices about how you want the spam filtering to be "
"set up. Afterwards it will automatically create the appropriate filter rules."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo vam da nekaj možnosti izbire, o tem, kako želite nastaviti "
"filtriranje neželene pošte. Nato bo samodejno ustvaril ustrezna pravila "
"filtriranja."

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:2409 using-kmail.docbook:2590
#, no-c-format
msgid "What are the limitations of the wizard?"
msgstr "Kaj so omejitve čarovnika?"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All it can do is set up the filters for you; it will provide a standard "
"setup. Manual modifications that have been applied to existing anti-spam "
"filters are not recognized. Instead, such filters are overwritten by the "
"wizard."
msgstr ""
"Vse, kar lahko naredi, je, da za vas nastavi filtre; na voljo bo standardna "
"nastavitev. Ročnih sprememb, ki so bile uporabljene za obstoječe filtre "
"proti nezaželeni pošti, ne prepoznava. Namesto tega čarovnik takšne filtre "
"prepiše."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can activate the wizard via <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Anti-Spam Wizard...</guisubmenu></menuchoice>. If this choice is "
"not available, click <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure &kmail;...</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Plugins</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and check the box next to <guilabel>Antispam</"
"guilabel>. You will be prompted to restart &kmail;; when you do, the wizard "
"will appear on the <guilabel>Tools</guilabel> menu."
msgstr ""
"Čarovnika lahko aktivirate prek <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Čarovnik za preprečevanje neželene pošte...</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>. Če ta izbira ni na voljo, kliknite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi &kmail;...</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Vtičniki</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in potrdite "
"polje poleg <guilabel>Proti neželeni pošti</guilabel>. Pozvan bo ponovni "
"zagon &kmail;-a ko to storite, se bo čarovnik pojavil v meniju "
"<guilabel>Orodja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The wizard scans for known anti-spam tools on your computer. It is also "
"possible to use the results of spam checks made by your service provider, by "
"evaluating header information which has been added to the messages. You can "
"let the wizard prepare &kmail; to use one or more of these in parallel. "
"However, note that anti-spam tool operations are unusually time consuming. "
"&kmail; can appear to be frozen during the scan of messages for spam, so you "
"may encounter problems with the responsiveness of &kmail;. Please consider "
"deleting the filter rules created by the wizard if the filtering becomes too "
"slow for you. (This has been a problem with older hardware. It probably "
"won't afflict more modern machines.)"
msgstr ""
"Čarovnik v računalniku poišče znana orodja za preprečevanje neželene pošte. "
"Prav tako je mogoče uporabiti rezultate preverjanja neželene pošte, ki ga "
"opravi vaš ponudnik storitev, in sicer tako, da ocenite informacije v glavi, "
"ki so bile dodane sporočilom. Čarovniku lahko dovolite, da pripravi &kmail; "
"za vzporedno uporabo enega ali več teh programov. Vendar upoštevajte, da so "
"postopki orodja za preprečevanje neželene pošte nenavadno dolgotrajni. "
"&kmail; se lahko med pregledovanjem sporočil za neželeno pošto zdi "
"zamrznjen, zato lahko naletite na težave z odzivnostjo &kmail;-a. Če "
"filtriranje postane prepočasno, razmislite o izbrisu pravil filtriranja, ki "
"jih je ustvaril čarovnik. (To je bila težava pri starejši strojni opremi. "
"Verjetno ne bo prizadela sodobnejših strojev.)"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2435
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here are some observations about a few anti-spam tools."
msgstr "Tukaj je nekaj opazk o nekaterih orodjih proti neželenim sporočilom."

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:2439
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bogofilter"
msgstr "Bogofilter"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bogofilter is a Bayesian filter. Its spam detection ability relies on an "
"initial training phase. On the other hand, it's a pretty fast tool. That's "
"why it is recommended for people who want fast spam detection, and who "
"aren't worried about putting some effort into the initial training, before "
"the detection rate increases significantly."
msgstr ""
"Bogofilter je Bayesov filter. Njegova sposobnost zaznavanja neželene pošte "
"temelji na začetni fazi usposabljanja. Po drugi strani pa je precej hitro "
"orodje. Zato ga priporočamo ljudem, ki želijo hitro zaznavanje neželene "
"pošte in jih ne skrbi, da bi se morali potruditi pri začetnem usposabljanju, "
"preden se stopnja zaznavanja znatno poveča."

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:2451
#, no-c-format
msgid "SpamAssassin"
msgstr "SpamAssassin"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"SpamAssassin is a fairly complex tool to use against spam. Although its "
"behavior depends heavily on its configuration, it can detect spam quite well "
"without any training. However, scanning a message takes a little longer "
"compared to pure Bayesian filters. Let's say it's not the tool of choice for "
"people without some background information about SpamAssassin's capabilities."
msgstr ""
"SpamAssassin je precej zapleteno orodje za preprečevanje neželene pošte. "
"Čeprav je njegovo obnašanje močno odvisno od njegove konfiguracije, lahko "
"precej dobro zazna neželeno pošto tudi brez usposabljanja. Vendar pa "
"pregledovanje sporočila v primerjavi s čistimi Bayesovimi filtri traja "
"nekoliko dlje. Recimo, da to ni najprimernejše orodje za ljudi, ki nimajo "
"informacij o zmožnostih programa SpamAssassin."

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:2463
#, no-c-format
msgid "Annoyance Filter"
msgstr "Annoyance Filter"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Perhaps not so often used until more distributions pick it up. It's clearly "
"a tool for specialists."
msgstr ""
"Morda se ne bo tako pogosto uporabljal, dokler ga ne bo prevzelo več "
"distribucij. To je očitno orodje za strokovnjake."

#. Tag: term
#: using-kmail.docbook:2471
#, no-c-format
msgid "GMX Spam Filter"
msgstr "GMX filter neželenih sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you get your mail via the GMX freemail provider, your messages have "
"already been scanned for spam. The result of that process is documented in a "
"special header field in each message. It's possible to use the content of "
"this header field to filter out spam. There is very little slowdown in the "
"filtering when this tool is used, as the messages have already been "
"processed by the external email server."
msgstr ""
"Če pošto prejemate prek ponudnika brezplačne pošte GMX, so bila vaša "
"sporočila že pregledana za neželeno pošto. Rezultat tega postopka je "
"dokumentiran v posebnem polju glave v vsakem sporočilu. Vsebino tega polja "
"glave je mogoče uporabiti za filtriranje neželene pošte. Pri uporabi tega "
"orodja je upočasnitev filtriranja zelo majhna, saj je sporočila že obdelal "
"zunanji e-poštni strežnik."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2488 using-kmail.docbook:2610
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Napredno"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; can use several external tools to detect spam messages; it will try "
"to automatically find out which tools are installed on your system, and will "
"display all of these in a list. The list is ordered by the average speed of "
"the filtering process of the tools. You can mark the tools which you want "
"&kmail; to utilize to detect spam. If you want more choices, you can simply "
"close the wizard, install a new tool, then restart the wizard."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; lahko za odkrivanje neželenih sporočil uporablja več zunanjih "
"orodij; poskuša samodejno ugotoviti, katera orodja so nameščena v vašem "
"sistemu, in jih prikaže na seznamu. Seznam je urejen glede na povprečno "
"hitrost postopka filtriranja orodij. Označite lahko orodja, ki jih želite, "
"da jih &kmail; uporabi za odkrivanje neželene pošte. Če želite več možnosti, "
"lahko čarovnika preprosto zaprete, namestite novo orodje in znova zaženete "
"čarovnika."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have marked at least one tool, &kmail; is able to provide filters "
"which allow the classification of the messages as spam or not spam. It will "
"also provide actions to let you manually classify messages. These actions "
"will be available in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Apply Filter &gt;</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu item, "
"and also via a pair of icons on the toolbar. If any of the tools you "
"selected support Bayesian filtering (&ie; a method to detect spam based on "
"statistical analysis of the messages) then these messages are not only "
"marked but additionally piped through the tools to help them learn, thereby "
"improving their detection rate."
msgstr ""
"Če ste označili vsaj eno orodje, &kmail; lahko zagotovi filtre, ki omogočajo "
"razvrstitev sporočil kot nezaželene ali nezaželene pošte. Na voljo bodo tudi "
"dejanja, s katerimi boste lahko ročno razvrščali sporočila. Ta dejanja bodo "
"na voljo v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Uporabi filter &gt;</guisubmenu></menuchoice> in tudi "
"prek para ikon v orodni vrstici. Če katero od izbranih orodij podpira "
"Bayesovo filtriranje (metoda za odkrivanje neželene pošte na podlagi "
"statistične analize sporočil), se ta sporočila ne le označijo, temveč se "
"dodatno posredujejo v orodja, da se lažje učijo in tako izboljšajo stopnjo "
"odkrivanja."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the second page, you will be able to select some additional actions to be "
"performed in &kmail; with regard to spam messages: if you want messages "
"detected as spam to be moved into a certain folder, select the appropriate "
"folder and mark the <guilabel>Move known spam to:</guilabel> option; if "
"messages detected as spam should additionally be marked as read, then mark "
"the <guilabel>Mark detected spam messages as read</guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"Na drugi strani boste lahko izbrali nekaj dodatnih dejanj, ki jih je treba "
"izvesti v &kmail;u v zvezi s sporočili neželene pošte: če želite, da se "
"sporočila, zaznana kot neželena, premaknejo v določeno mapo, izberite "
"ustrezno mapo in označite možnost <guilabel>Premakni znana neželena "
"sporočila v:</guilabel>; če je treba sporočila, zaznana kot neželena, "
"dodatno označiti kot prebrana, označite možnost <guilabel>Označi zaznana "
"neželena sporočila kot prebrana</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting at least one of the available tools will allow the wizard to "
"finish the filter setup. The wizard will not take any modifications in "
"existing filters, formerly created by it, into consideration, but will "
"either append new filters or replace existing filters. In any case you may "
"want to inspect the result of this process in the <link linkend=\"filter-"
"dialog\">Filter Dialog</link>. The wizard will also create toolbar buttons "
"for marking messages as spam or as ham. Keep in mind that classifying "
"messages as spam will also move those messages to the folder you have "
"specified for spam messages, when you select the <quote>spam</quote> option."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete vsaj eno od razpoložljivih orodij, bo čarovnik dokončal "
"nastavitev filtra. Čarovnik ne bo upošteval sprememb obstoječih filtrov, ki "
"jih je prej ustvaril, temveč bo dodal nove filtre ali zamenjal obstoječe. V "
"vsakem primeru boste morda želeli pregledati rezultat tega postopka v <link "
"linkend=\"filter-dialog\">Pogovornem oknu filtra</link>. Čarovnik bo "
"ustvaril tudi gumbe v orodni vrstici za označevanje sporočil kot neželene "
"pošte ali zaželene pošte. Ne pozabite, da se bodo sporočila, ki jih "
"razvrstite med neželeno pošto, premaknila tudi v mapo, ki ste jo določili za "
"neželena sporočila, ko izberete možnost <quote>neželeno sporočilo</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some More Details for Experts"
msgstr "Nekaj dodatnih podrobnosti za eksperte"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2535
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The wizard uses information stored in a special configuration file named "
"<filename>kmail.antispamrc</filename> (stored in the global or local &kde; "
"config directory). It will first check the global config file and then the "
"local config file. If the local config file contains an entry with a higher "
"(newer) version number, the configuration data from the local file (for that "
"tool) is used, so both administrators and users can update the wizard's "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"Čarovnik uporablja informacije, shranjene v posebni konfiguracijski datoteki "
"z imenom <filename>kmail.antispamrc</filename> (shranjena v splošnem ali "
"krajevnem imeniku &kde; config). Najprej bo preveril splošno datoteko z "
"nastavitvami in nato krajevno datoteko z nastavitvami. Če krajevna datoteka "
"z nastavitvami vsebuje vnos z višjo (novejšo) številko različice, se "
"uporabijo nastavitveni podatki iz lokalne datoteke (za to orodje), tako da "
"lahko tako skrbniki kot uporabniki posodobijo nastavitve čarovnika."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The local detection of spam messages is achieved by creating <guilabel>pipe "
"through</guilabel> actions per-tool within a special filter. Another filter "
"contains rules to check for detected spam messages and actions to mark them "
"and (optionally, depending on the choice in the wizard) to move them into a "
"folder. Both filters are configured to be applied to incoming messages and "
"for manual filtering."
msgstr ""
"Krajevno zaznavanje neželenih sporočil se doseže z ustvarjanjem "
"dejanj<guilabel>pošlji skozi</guilabel> za posamezno orodje v posebnem "
"filtru. Drug filter vsebuje pravila za preverjanje zaznanih neželenih "
"sporočil in ukrepe za njihovo označevanje ter (po želji, odvisno od izbire v "
"čarovniku) premikanje v mapo. Oba filtra sta nastavljena za uporabo za "
"dohodna sporočila in za ročno filtriranje."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Two filters are needed for the classification of ham and spam. They contain "
"actions to mark the messages appropriately. As mentioned above, the filter "
"for classification as spam can have another supplementary action to move the "
"messages into a predefined folder. If the selected tools support Bayesian "
"filtering, the wizard will create additional filter actions to pass the "
"messages to the tools (via <guilabel>Execute Command</guilabel> actions) in "
"the appropriate learning mode."
msgstr ""
"Za razvrščanje želene in neželene pošte sta potrebna dva filtra. Vsebujeta "
"ukrepe za ustrezno označevanje sporočil. Kot je navedeno zgoraj, ima lahko "
"filter za razvrstitev med neželeno pošto še eno dodatno dejanje, da se "
"sporočila premaknejo v vnaprej določeno mapo. Če izbrana orodja podpirajo "
"Bayesovo filtriranje, bo čarovnik ustvaril dodatna dejanja filtriranja za "
"posredovanje sporočil orodjem (prek dejanja <guilabel>Izvedi ukaz</"
"guilabel>) v ustreznem načinu učenja."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to fine-tune the filtering process, you might be interested in "
"the chapter about <link linkend=\"filter-optimization\">Filter Optimization</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite natančno prilagoditi postopek filtriranja, vas bo morda zanimalo "
"poglavje o <link linkend=\"filter-optimization\">Optimizacija filtra</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2569
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Anti-Virus Wizard"
msgstr "Protivirusni čarovnik"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; does not have a built-in virus detection solution: the developers "
"believe using external, but specialized, tools is the better approach. "
"&kmail; uses these tools through its flexible filter architecture. The Anti-"
"Virus Wizard helps you with the initial filter setup."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; nima vgrajene rešitve za odkrivanje virusov: razvijalci menijo, da "
"je boljši pristop uporaba zunanjih, vendar specializiranih orodij. &kmail; "
"uporablja ta orodja prek svoje prilagodljive arhitekture filtrov. Čarovnik "
"za protivirusne programe vam pomaga pri začetni nastavitvi filtra."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It will give you some choices about how you want virus filtering to be set "
"up. Afterwards it will automatically create the appropriate filter rules."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo vam bo nekaj možnosti izbire, glede tega kako želite nastaviti "
"filtriranje virusov. Nato bo čarovnik samodejno ustvaril ustrezna pravila "
"filtriranja."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2592
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All it can do is set up the filters for you; it will provide a standard "
"setup. Manual modifications that have been applied to existing anti-virus "
"filters are not recognized. Instead, such filters are overwritten by the "
"wizard."
msgstr ""
"Vse, kar lahko naredi, je, da za vas nastavi filtre; na voljo bo standardna "
"nastavitev. Ročnih sprememb, ki so bile uporabljene za obstoječe "
"protivirusne filtre, ne prepoznava. Namesto tega čarovnik takšne filtre "
"prepiše."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can activate the wizard via <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Anti-Virus Wizard...</guisubmenu></menuchoice>. If this choice "
"is not available, click <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure &kmail;...</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Plugins</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and check the box next to <guilabel>Antivirus</"
"guilabel>. You will be prompted to restart &kmail;; when you do, the wizard "
"will appear on the <guilabel>Tools</guilabel> menu."
msgstr ""
"Čarovnika lahko aktivirate prek <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Protivirusni čarovnik...</guisubmenu></menuchoice>. Če ta izbira "
"ni na voljo, kliknite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi &kmail;...</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Vtičniki</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in potrdite polje poleg <guilabel>Proti virusom</"
"guilabel>. Pozvan bo ponovni zagon &kmail;-a. Ko to storite, se bo čarovnik "
"pojavil v meniju <guilabel>Orodja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Anti-Virus Wizard basically works the same way as the <link linkend="
"\"the-anti-spam-wizard\">Anti-Spam Wizard</link> does. &kmail; can use "
"several external tools to detect messages containing viruses. It will "
"determine which of these tools are installed on your system, and will show "
"you the results from the search. You can mark the tools which you want "
"&kmail; to use for virus detection. If you want more choices, you can simply "
"close the wizard, install a new tool, then restart the wizard."
msgstr ""
"Čarovnik za protivirusne programe deluje na enak način kot <link linkend="
"\"the-anti-spam-wizard\">Čarovnik proti neželeni pošti</link>. &kmail; lahko "
"za odkrivanje sporočil, ki vsebujejo viruse, uporablja več zunanjih orodij. "
"Ugotovil bo, katera od teh orodij so nameščena v vašem sistemu, in prikazal "
"rezultate iskanja. Označite lahko orodja, ki jih želite uporabiti za "
"odkrivanje virusov. Če želite več možnosti, lahko čarovnika preprosto "
"zaprete, namestite novo orodje in znova zaženete čarovnika."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2622
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have chosen at least one tool you will be able to select actions for "
"&kmail; to perform on messages containing viruses. To let &kmail; detect "
"messages containing viruses, you should mark the <guilabel>Check messages "
"using the anti-virus tools</guilabel> option. If you want messages infected "
"by a virus to be moved into a certain folder, select the appropriate folder "
"and mark the <guilabel>Move detected viral messages to the selected folder</"
"guilabel> option. If such messages should also be marked as read, select the "
"<guilabel>Additionally, mark detected viral messages as read</guilabel> "
"option."
msgstr ""
"Če ste izbrali vsaj eno orodje, boste lahko izbrali ukrepe, ki jih bo "
"&kmail; izvedel za sporočila, ki vsebujejo viruse. Če želite, da &kmail; "
"zazna sporočila, ki vsebujejo viruse, morate označiti možnost "
"<guilabel>Preveri sporočila z uporabo protivirusnih orodij</guilabel>. Če "
"želite, da se sporočila, okužena z virusom, premaknejo v določeno mapo, "
"izberite ustrezno mapo in označite možnost <guilabel>Premakni zaznana "
"okužena sporočila v izbrano mapo</guilabel>. Če je treba takšna sporočila "
"označiti tudi kot prebrana, izberite možnost <guilabel>Dodatno označi "
"odkrita virusna sporočila kot prebrana</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting at least one of these options will allow the wizard to finish the "
"filter setup. The wizard will not take any existing filter rules into "
"account, but will append new rules. In any case you may want to inspect the "
"result of this process in the <link linkend=\"filter-dialog\">Filter Dialog</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete vsaj eno od teh možnosti, bo čarovnik dokončal nastavitev "
"filtra. Čarovnik ne bo upošteval obstoječih pravil filtriranja, temveč bo "
"dodal nova pravila. V vsakem primeru boste morda želeli pregledati rezultat "
"tega postopka v <link linkend=\"filter-dialog\">Pogovornem oknu filtra</"
"link>."

#. Tag: title
#: using-kmail.docbook:2642
#, no-c-format
msgid "Details"
msgstr "Podrobnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2644
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The wizard uses information stored in a special configuration file named "
"<filename>kmail.antivirusrc</filename> (stored in the global or local &kde; "
"config directory). If the local config file contains an entry with a higher "
"(newer) version number, the configuration data from the local file (for that "
"tool) is used, so both administrators and users can update the wizard's "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"Čarovnik uporablja informacije, shranjene v posebni nastavitveni datoteki z "
"imenom <filename>kmail.antivirusrc</filename> (shranjena v splošni ali "
"krajevni mapi &kde; nastavitev). Če krajevna datoteka z nastavitvami vsebuje "
"vnos z višjo (novejšo) številko različice, se uporabijo nastavitveni podatki "
"iz krajevne datoteke (za to orodje), tako da lahko tako skrbniki kot "
"uporabniki posodobijo nastavitve čarovnika."

#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:2652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The detection of messages containing viruses is achieved by creating "
"<guilabel>pipe through</guilabel> actions per-tool within a special filter. "
"Another filter contains rules to check for infected messages, and actions to "
"mark them and (optionally, depending on the choice in the wizard) to move "
"them into a folder. Both filters are configured to be applied to incoming "
"messages and for manual filtering."
msgstr ""
"Odkrivanje sporočil, ki vsebujejo viruse, se doseže z ustvarjanjem "
"<guilabel>pošlji skozi</guilabel> dejanj za posamezno orodje v posebnem "
"filtru. Drugi filter vsebuje pravila za preverjanje okuženih sporočil in "
"ukrepe za njihovo označevanje ter (po želji, odvisno od izbire v čarovniku) "
"premikanje v mapo. Oba filtra sta nastavljena za uporabo za dohodna "
"sporočila in za ročno filtriranje."

